apps.title: Bobby Approved - Food Scanner
apps.description:
Bobby Approved is a free food scanner app that instantly shows if a food product is good for your health or not. Learn how to buy the best quality products from the grocery store with the Bobby Approved app. Just point your camera, scan the barcode, and find out if that box of pasta, loaf of bread, or box of cereal is made with best-in-class ingredients, or if you should put it back.

The bad ingredients are highlighted in red, and by tapping on them you can learn why. Bobby has spend years researching ingredients in products and their potential health impact and has created a list of over 100 harmful ingredients, which is available to explore no the app.

If you are one of the 12+ million people who follow Bobby @flavcity, you know he has an unwavering dedication to helping people put the best quality foods in their body. For years Bobby has been making videos at the most popular grocery stores in the country and now with this free app you can take the guesswork out of shopping. It’s like shopping alongside Bobby!


Using the food scanner app is super easy:
- Scan any food barcode to see if a product is Bobby approved or not, and why. The harmful ingredients are highlighted in red.
- Tap on each ingredient to understand its health impact.
- Search products, ingredients, or browse products by store.
- If a product is not Bobby Approved, the app will give you healthy alternatives.

Ingredients we flag:
Bobby has flagged over 100 ingredients in our database as potentially harmful. All of these flagged ingredients are backed by scientific studies and include natural and artificial flavors, fake sugars, food dyes, chemical additives, inflammatory seed oils, preservatives and more. By identifying these additives in your food, you can shop for yourself and family with confidence. Our products and ingredients library are continuously updated with new products and data.

Better ingredient handling and allergens display
Redesigned tab bar and My Profile screen
UI refinements, stability and performance fixes

Are you hungry?

Need grocery shopping in minutes?

Do you want your daily needs at your door without leaving your home?

Download the app, sign up for free. After choosing your location, order your food, market or daily needs quickly!


What awaits you at Yemeksepeti?

-Thousands of discounts every day for your food, grocery and daily needs!

All you have to do is think about your needs and take a look at the options around you!

apps.title: Wolt Delivery: Food and more
apps.description:
Enjoy your favorite restaurants and stores, all in one place.
The Wolt app makes it easy to discover and order (almost) anything from your city. From delicious food and fresh groceries to pharmacy and pet supplies. Search by category, cuisine, restaurant or item! You can easily browse popular restaurants including McDonald's, KFC, Domino's, Pizza Hut, Papa Johns, Burger King and many more. Enjoy food delivery of burgers, pizza, sushi and other delicious items. If you prefer, you can pick up your order from the restaurant or store!

Order (almost) anything, on-demand.
Need to stock up on groceries? Can’t make it to the city? Wolt has you covered with groceries and essentials at your fingertips. Browse through the categories on Wolt and order anything, from pharmacy items to pet supplies. Anything you need, we’ve got you covered with our 40 000+ restaurants and stores. 

Top offers, only on Wolt.
Discover great offers on food, groceries and more! Browse hand-picked deals in the Wolt app and enjoy great savings. There’s offers on everything from food and groceries to electronics and homewares. Find the freshest deals in the app, including up to 50% off your order and €0 delivery fees!


Subscribe to Wolt+
If you’re looking for even bigger savings, Wolt+ is our popular subscription service offering €0 delivery fees, plus much more. As a Wolt+ member, you’ll unlock unbeatable deals and exclusive perks.

Make every occasion special with Wolt
We’ve made it easy to order and enjoy whatever you need. Get gifts for your loved ones, schedule orders for groceries and food, and save with deals on clothing and more! Wolt has you covered with everything to make moments special. Browse the selection of lovely flowers, chocolates, baked treats and more – delivered to your door in one hour or less.

Double Order
Need to order groceries and dinner? Now you can! Combine two local venues in one order with the same delivery fee. Place a Double Order and enjoy more convenience, for less!

Track every step
With every order, you can enjoy real-time tracking, and a minute-by-minute countdown. Whether you keep an eye on the tracker, or have other things to do, we'll keep you notified, so you know when your order is about to arrive.

Customer support
If something doesn’t go as planned, we’re ready to help – with customer support available 24/7. Our friendly team is there to help the 25+ countries we operate in and are ready to respond in seconds.

Payment
We think ordering Wolt should be as simple as possible. That’s why you can pay conveniently and securely with your credit card or Apple Pay. Whatever works for you.

Life simplified. Joy delivered. 
Wolt is currently available in 170+ cities located in Azerbaijan, Croatia, Cyprus, Czechia, Denmark, Estonia, Finland, Georgia, Germany, Greece, Hungary, Israel, Japan, Kazakhstan, Latvia, Lithuania, Malta, Norway, Poland,  Serbia,  Slovakia, Slovenia, Sweden. More are added all the time! Download Now and Unlock Essentials at your fingertips.

Wolt is an Editors’ Choice! 
Recognized by Apple as a top-rated app, Wolt delivers more than just food. Enjoy a seamless experience, from browsing our curated selection of restaurants to tracking your order in real-time.

apps.title: Whole Foods Market
apps.description:
Browse sales, order lunch and dinner, discover products, and build your shopping list — all in the Whole Foods Market app.




Scan Your In-Store Code
Now the In-Store Code does even more. Scan to apply Prime savings for an extra 10% off sale items (excluding alcohol) plus special deals on seasonal favorites. You can even scan your code at the register to pay at select stores. No service? No problem. Access the code offline.



Browse Sales
Discover weekly sales from your local store, then save them to your shopping list to make your next trip even easier. Prime members get an extra 10% off hundreds of weekly sale prices (excluding alcohol). Just scan your In-Store Code in the app at checkout.



Get Items Shipped
No store near you? No problem. You can now shop your favorite Whole Foods Market pantry go-tos, essential paper products, everyday snacks and more, shipped FREE with Amazon Prime.



Order Meals
Order meals for delivery or pickup at your local store, and easily reorder your favorites. Select from our signature items or customize your hot pizza, sandwich, salad, soup and more. Available in select stores.


Discover Product Selection
Search for specific products available in your local store and filter results to find sales, local brands, special dietary selection and more. Add products directly to your list while browsing.



Create a Shopping List
Easily build your grocery shopping list by adding all of the items you need. Powered by Alexa Shopping List, items are automatically grouped by department so you can quickly find them in-store.




By using this app, you agree to the Conditions of Use.

raw_data.releaseNotes: Bug fixes and minor improvements.

apps.title: Chowdeck | Food Delivery
apps.description:
At Chowdeck, we deliver happiness straight to you, one delicious meal at a time.

Africa’s leading on-demand online food delivery service, Chowdeck, offers quick and convenient food delivery from hundreds of your favourite restaurants! Browse our extensive food menu, order food online, and enjoy fast and reliable delivery right to your door. Say goodbye to long queues and waiting time with Chowdeck!

Enjoy a variety of cuisines, including:

- African & Fast Food (Jollof rice, Pasta, Burgers, Waakye, Kelewele)
- Asian (Chinese, Indian, Japanese, and Lebanese)
- Drinks (Alcoholic and Non-Alcoholic)
- Mexican (Tacos)
- Halal friendly
- Healthy / Vegetarian (Breakfast, Smoothies, Fresh Fruit Juices)
- Pastries (Cakes, Cookies, Meat pies, Sausage rolls) and more.

Eat your favourite meals where you like! Chowdeck delivers food in numerous cities in Accra, Lagos and Abuja, including Yaba, Alausa, Ikoyi, Ogudu, Wuse, Gwarinpa, Lekki, Victoria Island, Ikeja, Surulere, Festac, Amuwo Odofin, Egbeda, Alimosho, Gbagada, Ikoyi, Jahi, Maitama, Garki, Jabi, Utako, Mabushi, Katampe, Kado Wuye, Apo, Gudu, Life Camp, 1st Avenue, Asokoro, Jahi, Wuse and Central Areas with ongoing expansions to other major cities across the continent.

With Chowdeck, order food online and get it delivered to you immediately or at a scheduled time. Alternatively, order ahead online and pick it up at your favourite restaurants.

Get notified from when the restaurant accepts your meal to when it arrives. Track your meal every second of the way between the restaurant and delivery.

Our restaurant partners include Honeysuckle, Papa's Pizza, Mega Chicken, Ajishafe, Burger King, Mama JB Takeout Restaurant, Jay’s Diner, King Glab, Korede Spaghetti, Panarotti’s Pizza, Fruits2Go, Amoke Oge, Saminu Kilishi, KFC, Debonair’s Pizza, Mr Biggs, Yakoyo, Labule, Red Gourmet Kitchen, El Padrino’s, Iyan Aladuke, The Place, Cubana Fish, DO Bowls, Food Fusion, Johnny Rocket, Papiees Maestro, Keje Grill, Ojuelegba Restaurant, So Fresh, Eden Life, Korean Wife’s Table, Squizz’d, Cookie Nation, Old English, and more.

Shop your groceries online easily from leading supermarkets, including Blenco, FoodCo and Domino Supermarket. Buy household needs, including beauty and cosmetics, self-care, baby food, pet needs, snacks, drinks, cleaning supplies and grocery staples such as bread, milk, chocolates, coffee, sugar, fruits, vegetables, frozen foods, and alcoholic beverages.

The Chowdeck Lifestyle is marked by ease and enjoyment. We offer our beloved customers unique perks like discounts, free delivery, and promotions through our in-app loyalty program and partnerships with local and international companies.

What are you waiting for? Order food online with Chowdeck and enjoy fast, convenient delivery wherever you are!

- Enter your location and find restaurants and supermarkets delivering to your location.
- Browse meals and products listed from restaurants and supermarkets near you.
- Pay online, sit back, and relax.
- Track your order in real-time in-app and through notifications.
- Rate and review your experience.

Any questions? Contact our Support team at https://chowdeck.com/contact

We are available on:
- Website - https://chowdeck.com
- Instagram - https://instagram.com/chowdeck
- Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/chowdeck
- Twitter - https://twitter.com/chowdeck
- TikTok - https://www.tiktok.com/@chowdeck

apps.title: Beyond Menu Food Delivery
apps.description:
Beyond Menu - Food Delivery

Find food for pickup or delivery from the best local restaurants near you.
 
Getting hungry? Order food from the best independent restaurants in your town and pay less while doing it. There are no hidden fees for you or your favorite restaurants, just low, transparent menu prices and good food. 
 
SUPPORT YOUR NEIGHBORHOOD
You won’t find big chains on Beyond Menu. We specifically work with independent restaurants to support local community restaurants and help diners find the best food in their area. Browse the menu and find some amazing food to order.
 
ORDER TAKEOUT OR DELIVERY
Choose from thousands of different local restaurants and over 25 different cuisines. It’s time you try something new and explore the restaurant community around you to see what you’ve been missing out on all this time. Order it for pickup or stay in and order food delivered to your door.
 
SIMPLE ORDERING & LOWER PRICES
We don’t charge you or the restaurant huge fees and that translates to lower menu prices. Order foods from local restaurants at a better price and get it done in just a few simple clicks. 
 
LOCAL COUPONS
It isn’t just about lower menu prices. Restaurants on Beyond Menu frequently offer coupons and free food. Get out and explore something new and you might get a free appetizer or other discount while you do it!
 
AVAILABLE ALL OVER THE USA
We work with independent restaurants so you can order the best local food no matter where you are! We’re in Baltimore, Denver, Los Angeles, New York, Phoenix, San Francisco, Boston, Houston, Miami, Omaha, Portland, Seattle, Chicago, Las Vegas, New Jersey, Philadelphia, San Diego, Washington DC, and more!

raw_data.releaseNotes:
- Introducing a new Home experience for a smoother and more intuitive interface
- Performance improvements and bug fixes to make your experience even better

apps.title: DiDi Food - Food Delivery
apps.description:
Are you craving sushi, pizza or a salad? 

With DiDi Food you can order from your favorite restaurants with just a tap of your finger! 

With more than 10 million orders delivered, we are experts to get you in minutes the food you want. 

In just 3 simple steps, you can enjoy delicious food without leaving your home: Open the DiDi Food app and choose your delivery address Choose your favorite restaurants, and select dishes from their menu Choose a payment method to submit the order, and your meal will be promptly delivered to your door by one of our couriers 

Very hungry? View stores according to the fastest delivery times and get your food as soon as possible. 

Very busy? Don't worry! With just a few clicks, you can order, pay and get your food delivered in minutes. 

Want to know your order's location? Track your order's entire real-time progress from ordering, to preparation, to delivery. 

You can even view your courier's location on the map At DiDi Food we want you to have the best experience. 

In case you need help, our support team will be happy to help you 365 days a year. 

Enjoy your meal!

apps.title: Thuisbezorgd.nl
apps.description:
With the Thuisbezorgd app, you can order whatever you love, wherever you are. With a wide variety of restaurants, supermarkets and convenience stores to choose from, you can enjoy everything from burgers, pizza, pasta, sushi, salads and loads more, and get it all delivered to your door.

Need some bits from the supermarket? Just open the app, choose ‘groceries’ and fill your basket. Whether it’s baby food, flowers, beer, wine, beauty products, ice cream, chocolate, milk, fruit and bread, our partners have it all.

How it works:
Ordering is easy. You can either pick a saved address, fill in your postcode/street name or let the app find your location automatically. You can then choose your favourite restaurant or store and select whatever you fancy. 

Follow your order to your doorstep:
Track your order from the kitchen or store straight to your doorstep with our Food Tracker®. We'll even send you push notifications to update you about the status of your order. It usually takes 30-45 minutes to deliver your food or groceries.

What you get with our app:
- Quick and hassle-free ordering
- Great offers and discounts
- Choose to pick up your order at the restaurant or store
- Re-order the same delicious meal with one tap of a button
- Browse grocery stores, cuisines, offers, best-rated restaurants, nearby spots and vegetarian/halal options
- Get regular updates on your order with our handy Food Tracker®
- Choose from multiple payment options

Order from big brands or local heroes. 
Thuisbezorgd has it all!

Based on your feedback, we improved the design. It’s easier than ever to order what you want – from groceries to delicious meals.
There are now more search options and filters, and we also improved the navigation speed.

On top of that, we added new features like:

- Loved in your area
Browse the most popular categories in your neighbourhood. 

- Bigger menu images
See what’s on offer at a glance. Like the look of something? Press ‘+’ to add it to your basket.

- Your cravings, saved
Your last order is saved for you, so you can come back to it anytime.

There are more exciting features coming up in the near future, so make sure you update your Thuisbezorgd app regularly!

Questions or tips? Contact us: iosapp@takeaway.com

apps.title: Food Fantasy
apps.description:
Food Fantasy is a “Food Personified” RPG adventure management game. Inspired by hundreds of recipes from around the world, a group of world renowned artists and voice actors have brought food to life. Giving them unique personalities, stories, looks and designs. In game, you’ll be able to engage in combat with your Food Souls, collect ingredients, develop recipes and create your very own world-class restaurant!      

Food Personified – Collect Food Souls
Collect Food Souls from around the world with unique personalities, traits& looks. Tiramisu, Boston Lobster, Spaghetti, Coffee and Red Win and many more waiting for you to encounter on your adventure! 

DIY Management – Create your unique restaurant 
Real restaurant simulator with hundreds of recipes for you to discover. Customize and decorate your restaurant with different furniture and designs. Complete take-out orders and prevent dine & dash customers. 
Build your very own 5-star restaurant!     

Amazing Voiceovers – Voice of Food Souls
Voiceovers done by a cast of world renowned Japanese Voice Actors! Miyuki Sawashiro, NatsukiHanae, Takuya Eguchi, Ayane Sakura, AyumuMurase,Kenshō Ono, Ayako Kawasumi,Aoi Yūki and many more talented actors using their voice to bring life to the Food Souls! 

Food Combos – Hundreds of Food Pairings
Tiramisu & Chocolate, Coffee & Milk, Steak & Red Wine and various otherpowerful and “delicious” combos for you to turn the tides of battle. Unique “Talents” and an everchanging “weather” system brings uncertainty and excitement during combat. 
Foodies, it’s time to put your skills to the test! 

PLEASE NOTE! Food Fantasy is free to download and play, however some game items can also be purchased for real money. If you do not want to use this feature, please set up password protection for purchases in the settings of your AppStore. Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Food Fantasy.

Have any questions or issues with the  game from Elex Tech? 
Reach us at: foodfantasy.help@gmail.com
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/foodfantasygame/

advisories: Infrequent/Mild Simulated Gambling

1.Add new activities and props

Food Personified – Collect Food Souls
Collect Food Souls from around the world with unique personalities, traits& looks. Tiramisu, Boston Lobster, Spaghetti, Coffee and Red Win and many more waiting for you to encounter on your adventure! 

DIY Management – Create your unique restaurant 
Real restaurant simulator with hundreds of recipes for you to discover. Customize and decorate your restaurant with different furniture and designs. Complete take-out orders and prevent dine & dash customers. 
Build your very own 5-star restaurant!     

Amazing Voiceovers – Voice of Food Souls
Voiceovers done by a cast of world renowned Japanese Voice Actors! Miyuki Sawashiro, NatsukiHanae, Takuya Eguchi, Ayane Sakura, AyumuMurase,Kenshō Ono, Ayako Kawasumi,Aoi Yūki and many more talented actors using their voice to bring life to the Food Souls! 

Food Combos – Hundreds of Food Pairings
Tiramisu & Chocolate, Coffee & Milk, Steak & Red Wine and various otherpowerful and “delicious” combos for you to turn the tides of battle. Unique “Talents” and an everchanging “weather” system brings uncertainty and excitement during combat. 
Foodies, it’s time to put your skills to the test!

The Best Asian Food Delivery!
Fantuan Delivery offers the largest selection of your favourite Asian restaurants and other local favourite cuisines delivered to your door, anytime and anywhere.
【Fantuan Delivery & Pick-up】
Bringing the taste of authentic Asian cuisines to your door. Browse from hundreds of local restaurants to traditional Asian restaurants in your city. Unsure of what to eat tonight? Let Fantuan help filter the restaurants you crave.
Promotions: Enjoy limited-time discounts and promo codes every day.
Self Pick-up: Order in advance on our app and pick up meals at restaurants. Skip the line, save more. (No delivery fee, no tips, no service charges.)
Exclusive Restaurants: Find restaurants exclusive to Fantuan.

【Dine-in Deals & Reviews】
Fantuan now offers exclusive dine-in discounts and vouchers at popular restaurants. Order ahead in the app, scan to redeem in-store – fast, simple, and more affordable.
More than just deals, Fantuan also features user reviews and photo notes to help you find the best-rated local spots and avoid disappointing experiences.
Now available in Vancouver, Toronto, New York, Los Angeles, Chicago and more cities.

Fantuan Errands
Need to deliver a parcel but don’t have the time? Or need to grab something from the store but don’t want to go out? Fantuan Errands can help. Whether it’s documents, flowers, keys, or groceries – just tell us what you need, and we’ll take care of it.
TT Mart

apps.title: Yandex Eats: food delivery
apps.description:
Food delivery service from grocery stores, cafes and restaurants

You can order both burgers and steaks, as well as products from grocery stores. Free delivery for your first order!

ALL NEARBY GROCERIES AND RESTAURANTS IN ONE APP
Get your groceries delivered from both popular stores and local markets. And for those who don't want to cook, you can find your favorite dishes from cafes and restaurants. In Yandex Eats, you can order a cooked pizza or ingredients for it.

ORDER FAST DELIVERY TO YOUR ADDRESS
Enter the delivery address — we will find the nearest store or restaurant to you and deliver the order as quickly as possible. On average food is delivered in 32 minutes after placing an order — even faster than you would get ready to go shopping.

TRACK YOUR ORDER 
In the app, you can find out the status of the order and the location of the courier.

USE FILTERS TO FIND EVERYTHING YOU NEED
With filters you can find a specific cuisine or dish with one click. “Burgers”, “Sushi”, “Pizza” — Yandex Eats has sets for every occasion.

DISCOUNTS AND SPECIAL OFFERS EVERY DAY 
In the app, you can place an order profitably: for example, get free delivery or a dish as a gift. In the section “Promotions” we collect the best offers from shops and restaurants every day.

Yandex Eats is an information service. Delivery zones, delivery times, and restaurant offers are limited. To learn more, go to eda.yandex. Fast delivery: the average order delivery time is 32 minutes according to data from January 18 to January 25, 2022.

apps.title: DIG INN | Seasonal, fresh food
apps.description:
10 points for every $1 spent when you order DIG for delivery or pickup on the DIG app. With our new DIG Rewards program, every purchase unlocks reward progress and points toward the next loyalty tier. 

Use the DIG app to get your lunch or dinner delivered fast, for free. Order food online, or simply see where your nearest restaurant is located and what’s on the menu. Save your favorite items or reorder from your order history to quickly satisfy your vegetable needs. 

Getting DIG has never been easier. Schedule orders for takeout, and we’ll let you know when to pick it up. Or, we’ll deliver your food directly to you.

EARN REWARDS

Earn and redeem rewards both in-store and online through the app.

CUSTOMIZE YOUR ORDER

Craving a bowl? Prefer farro over rice? Feeling more greens over charred chicken? Build your own meal. We’ll take care of the rest.

FIND YOUR NEAREST DIG

If you’re looking for food in New York, Boston, Philadelphia, or a few other select locations, we can show you your closest restaurant.

BROWSE THE MENU

Our menu changes seasonally with what we can get our hands on — so make sure to check out the menu to see what we’re offering. Our menu also shows our many vegan food options, as well as allergy warnings.

TRACK YOUR PURCHASES

Really into what you ordered the last time, but can’t quite remember what it was? Take a look, and order it again.

EAT MORE VEGETABLES

They just taste good — especially when they’re delivered to your doorstep.

Questions or concerns? Find us on Facebook (facebook.com/diginnmarket), Twitter (@diginn), and Instagram (@diginn), or email (contact@diginn.com).

apps.title: Seamless: Local Food Delivery
apps.description:
When in doubt, go for takeout—Seamless has it all. Plus, fun fact: Seamless is powered by Grubhub! Order food delivery from thousands of restaurants, including local spots and national chains, and get groceries delivered too. Prefer pickup? No problem. Know the fees upfront and track orders from Seamless delivery partners in real time. The only surprise is just how easy takeout can be. 

ORDER FROM THOUSANDS OF RESTAURANTS
With Seamless, you can order takeout from your favorite local restaurants and everyone’s favorite chains. There are so many good eats out there, but you obviously deserve the best. Seamless makes it easier to choose your next meal with restaurant ratings and reviews. French fries, pizza, burritos, burgers, sushi, donuts—it’s all here, whenever a craving strikes. 

GET GROCERIES DELIVERED TOO
Think beyond your breakfast, lunch, and dinner orders. Seamless offers the ultimate convenience with grocery delivery, in addition to restaurant takeout. Order milk, bread, snacks, and frozen foods, as well as household essentials like paper towels and laundry detergent, from local convenience stores.  

EXPECT TO SEE THE FEES UPFRONT
Seamless gives it to you straight. See the delivery fee upfront, before you start crafting the perfect food order. Pay your way with credit cards, Seamless gift cards, or Venmo.

SKIP DELIVERY FEES
The key is Grubhub+. Sign up for unlimited $0 delivery fees on eligible orders, and enjoy exclusive offers and rewards as a Grubhub+ member.* Try Grubhub+ free for 30 days, then level up for just $9.99/month. The truth is, food tastes even better when you spend less on delivery. See details below.

TRACK DELIVERY IN REAL TIME
Seamless puts your delivery on the map. Track eligible orders in real time, from the restaurant to your front door, and know the moment your bacon-egg-and-cheese arrives. Every delivery is a special delivery with Seamless. 

COUNT ON THE SEAMLESS GUARANTEE
Get your food delivered on time and at the lowest price. Guaranteed, or we’ll make it right. Terms apply. See details: seamless.com/help/contact-us/learn-about-guarantee

YOU DO YOU AND SEAMLESS DELIVERS
Seamless serves up a personalized app experience, so you can reorder that feast you’re still thinking about from two months ago. Order sauce on the side, go for extra pickles, lose the onions—Seamless gets you. Are you a regular? Get rewarded when you come back for more at the same restaurants. You can also plan ahead by pre-ordering food for pickup or delivery. 

ORDER FROM NATIONAL RESTAURANTS
Sometimes you need a sure thing, and that’s why Seamless partners with national restaurants to offer the takeout food you know and love. Get delivery from Applebee’s, Arby’s, Buffalo Wild Wings, Burger King, Chick-fil-A, Chipotle, Denny’s, Dunkin’, Five Guys, IHOP, McDonald’s, KFC, Panda Express, Panera, Papa John’s, Popeyes, Shake Shack, Subway, Taco Bell, Wendy’s, White Castle, and more.

GET SUPPORT WHEN YOU NEED IT
Burning questions? Delivery crisis? Seamless customer support is here for you 24/7. 

*$0 delivery fees only apply to eligible delivery orders from Grubhub+ merchants that meet the subtotal minimum (before tax, tip, and fees) on the applicable menu page or otherwise indicated on the Grubhub platform. Additional fees may apply. 5% pickup credit applicable on eligible future pickup orders only and is calculated based on the qualifying order subtotal. Credit is not transferable, not redeemable for cash, expires 90 days after most recent credit is issued and is subject to restrictions. Grubhub+ is an automatically renewing membership service requiring recurring payments. After your free trial ends, your free trial will convert to a paid Grubhub+ membership and Grubhub will automatically charge you each month at the then-current rate (currently $9.99) plus tax until you cancel. See Grubhub+ cancellation and refund policy and full terms at https://lp.grubhub.com/legal/plus/

apps.title: 99: Rides, Food, Pay
apps.developer: 99 Taxis Desenvolvimento de Softwares Ltda. - Epp
apps.description:
99 is the biggest Brazilian e-hailing app. Our mission is to revolutionize mobility and transform people's lives. With few taps, you can request a car or taxi and also decide how you pay for it, whether it's with cash or straight in the app, where you'll have access to exclusive promotions!

Why request a 99 ride?

Power of choice
We have several options for you to choose how to move around in your city. Cars with private drivers, taxis or rides billed to your company through our corporate vouchers. Every moment in our day to day asks for a specific solution and it's you who is in control. Where are we going today?

Safety first
99's partner drivers go through a rigorous selection process. They rely on in-person and online training to ensure all the safety and comfort you deserve. The cars are comfortable and inspected, and of course, we keep a close eye on the passengers' ratings. That reminds us: don't forget to rate your last ride!

Fair rates
Our service is the most cost saving option in the city. And since transparency is one of our key values, we will always provide you with an estimate of how much you'll pay before you request your car. And with our newest feature, you can also track your POP ride's price in real time during your ride!

Smart-wallet
99's coupons are smart! If you have more than one in your wallet, the app itself shows you the best discount before ordering your car and applies it automatically. Keep an eye on your message inbox and do not miss any of them. To enjoy our fantastic discounts, you must register a card or PayPal account in the app.

Easy to use
Just open the app, choose your destination and you're done! 99 has the best technology in the world to find the right driver for you, and in minutes a car will arrive at your doorstep. Also, talk for free with the driver, by text or audio, using the new feature chat within the app.

Feeling like driving with 99? Come join us! Download 99 app for drivers and register here: http://m.onelink.me/85a6df7c

apps.title: Caviar - Order Food Delivery
apps.description:
Get food delivered from curated lists of local restaurants right at your fingertips with Caviar. Enjoy quality dining at home and make any night a special occasion.

Your first delivery is free. Also, receive $10 off your first order with the code TENONFOOD on orders of $35 or more.

TRUSTED AND EXCLUSIVE RESTAURANTS
Choose from many popular local restaurants and exclusive eateries you won't find on other delivery services -- from local mom-and-pop to Michelin-rated and The Infatuation picks!

DEALS AND SPECIALS
Regularly check in our app for new restaurants, special deals, and exclusive benefits. If you are a DoorDash DashPass member, you can use those benefits on Caviar, too!

NO-CONTACT DELIVERY
Deliveries are now left at your door by default and you have the choice to select "Hand it to me" if you prefer. If a no-contact delivery is requested, the Dasher will know you want them to leave your food in a safe place and alert you when it's ready for pickup.

REAL-TIME TRACKING
See when your order will arrive. From food quality to prep-times to traffic to weather, we've factored in all the elements that come between you and your food.

SCHEDULE DELIVERIES
Advance ordering allows you to get your food when it's most convenient for you.

NO MINIMUMS
Order as little or as much as you want.

apps.description:
Urbanspoon (by Zomato) for iPhone is the #1 FREE app dedicated to helping you find the best food and dining experiences at over a million restaurants.

apps.title: EatStreet Local Food Delivery
apps.description:
Take the quickest shortcut from hungry to happy with the EatStreet iOS app for food delivery & takeout.

Life’s easy with EatStreet - breakfast, brunch, lunch, dinner, or snacks - you don’t have to worry about it. The EatStreet food delivery app is your craving quencher for meals, drinks, snacks, appetizers and shareable food for parties: Available in over 250 cities throughout the U.S.! We offer fast pickup and food delivery from local restaurants and diners.
 
Our fast-growing EatStreet restaurant delivery app offers cheap food delivery in major cities including: 
-Illinois - DeKalb; 
-Iowa - Ames, Dubuque, Waterloo/Cedar Falls; 
-Kansas - Lawrence, Manhattan, Salina, Topeka; 
-Wisconsin - Appleton, Eau Claire, Fond du Lac WI, Green Bay, Janesville, Kenosha, La Crosse, Madison, Manitowoc, Milwaukee, Oshkosh, Sheboygan, Stevens Point, Wausau.

EatStreet partners with many local and chain restaurants in your city, neighborhood, or college town to provide diverse food choices: pizza, pasta, burgers, wings, tacos, etc. Some of our favorite food spots include Applebee's, Taco Johns, Toppers Pizza, Potbelly, Qdoba, Noodles & Company, Dairy Queen, Kwik Trip/Kwik Star and many more.

Order from home or work - just for yourself, or surprise everyone with a delicious treat! Need a celebratory cake or donuts at work? We’ve got you covered!

Dig into our hunger-solving Apple App features:

1. EatStreet Exclusive Coupons:
When you order food with the EatStreet App, we'll hook you up with exclusive coupons, restaurant specials, and rewards. We partner with many popular local restaurants from mom-&-pop diners to the big brands that everyone knows and loves. So the more you order to eat, the more you earn!  

2. Explore Different Cuisines: 
Order Chinese food; Get pizza delivered; Find your favorite sushi and pad thai; No matter what kind of food you crave, we've got you covered - Italian, Chinese, Mexican, Mediterranean, keto, vegetarian, vegan, pescatarian, gluten free and more!
 
3. Food Photography & Restaurant Reviews: 
Check out local favorite dishes and menu items before you order! You can even check-out photos of some of the tasty eats & read restaurant reviews to take the guessing out of what you're getting. 
 
4. Track Food Orders: 
There's no worse feeling after ordering food than not knowing where your order is. With our new EatStreet Food Order Tracker, you can check the status of your grub from the second you place your order until it's at your front door.  

5. Convenient Payment Options:  
The EatStreet iOS App offers a variety of ways to pay. You can always use credit card or PayPal, as well as using secure Apple Pay! Our EatStreet food ordering app allows you to pay for your meal as a group or an individual: great for work, parties and get-togethers.
 
6. Multiple Ways to Order Food:
Order Again: Having food deja? Our ‘Order Again’ feature makes it incredibly easy to reorder your favorite dishes.
Group Ordering & Split the Bill: Invite friends and start a group order. We’ll even split the bill so you don't get stuck ponying up for the "I'll pay you back later" people.
Order Ahead: Need food in the future? Place a delivery pickup order in advance. Your food will be piping hot and ready, right when and where you want it to be.
 
Ready to order with EatStreet? Here’s how to get started with your first food delivery:

  1. Download EatStreet iOS delivery app today!
  2. Create your account and login
  3. Pick from your favorite food spots
  4. Choose your meal and delivery type
  5. Pay and place your food order
  6. Track your delivery progress
  7. Enjoy your delicious food.

EatStreet is the perfect food ordering app for all your favorite grub & local eats. Order the meal you crave from local restaurants you love. Download the EatStreet food delivery app now!

Hungry. Happy. EatStreet.

raw_data.releaseNotes: Thanks for choosing EatStreet as your shortcut from hungry to happy! We update our app to improve your experience with faster and more reliable performance. This update introduces the EatStreet Cashback program and makes updates to our payment processor. Download the latest update today to check out the newest restaurants, app features, exclusive offers & more!

apps.title: Favor: Texas Food Delivery
apps.description:
Favor is the delivery app made by Texans, for Texans. From an extra-hot latte that meets you at the office to queso delivered (almost) right to your couch, we’re here when y’all are hungry.

Texans’ must-have membership
- Subscribe to the best of Texas with Favor Gold! Packed with uniquely local savings and perks, it’s everything you love about Texas, made even better.
- Members enjoy unlimited $0 delivery fees on almost everything in the app, monthly H-E-B savings, discounts for supporting local, reduced service fees, and much more.
- Try Favor Gold and enjoy 30 days free for a limited time!

PROUDLY PART OF H-E-B
- Experience the quality, value, selection, and service you expect from H-E-B in every single delivery.
- Available exclusively in the Favor app, H-E-B Now is the easiest way to get last-minute groceries right when you need them.
- Get restaurants for when you’re hungry now and groceries for when you’re hungry later—all in one place. Update to the latest version of the app to shop H-E-B Now and all your other in-store favorites!
- Delivery fees are always $0 from H-E-B-owned restaurants and stores, including H-E-B Beer & Wine, True Texas BBQ, and Blooms by H-E-B!
- H-E-B Visa® cardholders also earn unlimited 5% cash back on every Favor order. 

THOUSANDS OF RESTAURANTS AND STORES
- Get the best selection of national and Texas-only restaurants—plus alcohol, flowers, and more—delivered in as little as 45 minutes.
- Support locally-owned businesses and give back to your community.
- Order from favorites like Burger King, McDonald’s, Buffalo Wild Wings, Papa John’s Pizza, Applebee’s, Whataburger, Panda Express, Church’s Chicken, Five Guys, Dairy Queen, California Pizza Kitchen, Firehouse Subs, Hooters, Jersey Mike’s Subs, Pei Wei, Romano’s Macaroni Grill, Urban Bricks Pizza, Velvet Taco, Zoës Kitchen, and more!

DELIVERY YOU CAN HANG YOUR HAT ON
- We’re committed to making sure your order is fresh, accurate, and on time (every time).

TRULY TEXAN HOSPITALITY 
- We’ll always treat your order with care because we’re food lovers who just happen to be food deliverers.
- Enjoy one-on-one service and personal updates from your Runner (that’s what we call Favor delivery drivers).

PROUDLY UNAVAILABLE IN 49 STATES
- As a homegrown Texas brand and part of the H-E-B family, we’re uniquely focused on serving fellow Texans in more than 400 cities across the Lone Star State.
- Abilene, Arlington, Austin, Baytown, Beaumont, Brownsville, College Station, Corpus Christi, Dallas, Denton, Fort Worth, Georgetown, Houston, Killeen, Lubbock, Midland, New Braunfels, Odessa, Port Arthur, San Antonio, San Marcos, Temple, and Waco are just a few of them!

5-STAR SUPPORT
- Want real help from a real person? Our Texas-based team is ready to assist you throughout your delivery experience.

The H-E-B Visa Signature® Credit Card is issued by First Electronic Bank, Member FDIC, pursuant to a license from Visa USA Inc. The H-E-B Credit Card is powered by Imprint Payments, Inc. See Rewards Program Terms and Conditions and Credit Program Cardholder Agreement on heb.com/credit.

Discover Fantuan, the premier platform designed for international communities across Canada, the US, Australia, and the UK. We connect you to the richness of your neighborhood through convenient services and exclusive local experiences – all in one place.

Dine-in Deals & Restaurant Discovery:
Save on Dining: Enjoy exclusive discounts and vouchers for popular restaurants. Order & pay in the app, scan to redeem in-store – simple and affordable.

Wide Range of Venues: Find deals for restaurants (Chinese, Hotpot, Bubble Tea), entertainment (KTV, Escape Rooms), and services (Salons, Spas, Pet Care).

apps.title: Flashfood - Grocery deals
apps.description:
Real food, realer prices. Flashfood gives you unbeatable deals on groceries at peak deliciousness. Want to save big on fruit, vegetables, meat, milk, cheese, pantry staples* and more? Skip the coupons, get the Flashfood app. Convenient same-day pick up.

********

ALWAYS SOMETHING NEW
With fresh deals added daily, you’ll find go-to staples and new foods to discover. From chicken wings to crab cakes, kiwis to strawberries*, Flashfood helps you switch up your meals. And if you don’t see your find today — check back tomorrow. We might surprise you.

THE FRESHEST DEALS IN TOWN
We partner with major grocery stores like Meijer, GIANT and Stop & Shop to score you savings close to home. Same-day pick up, no long lines — just unbeatable deals. The real question is: how will you fit it all in the fridge?

WHO SHOULD USE FLASHFOOD?
People who eat food. That’s who. And people who love a great deal. And a great meal. 

HOW DOES IT WORK? WE’RE GLAD YOU ASKED
1. Download Flashfood and create an account
2. Browse grocery deals at nearby stores
3. Add items to your cart and buy in the app
4. Pick up your haul from the Flashfood Zone at your local partner store

WARNING: Upon finding your first amazing flash deal, spontaneous dancing for joy may occur.

WHAT’S THE CATCH? 
There’s no catch! Grocers are working hard to end food waste. By selling meat, produce, and prepared foods at big discounts on Flashfood, our partners ensure that surplus items – whether seasonal, overstocked, or nearing expiration — end up on dinner tables, not in the landfill. 

********

*Item selection varies by store. Terms and conditions apply. See details: flashfood.com/terms

Need help? We’re here. Reach out on live chat from the app or email us at support@flashfood.com.

We care about your privacy (for real). Read about it at flashfood.com/privacy 

To learn more about our impact, where we operate, and our plans for the future, visit flashfood.com.

apps.title: AteMate Food Journal (Ate)
apps.description:
Tired of the endless diet rollercoaster? You're not alone. That frustrating cycle of counting calories, feeling guilty, and constantly "starting over." Diets fail because they ignore what truly matters: a simple, mindful approach to food and self-care.

AteMate is the mindful food diary built to help you finally break free. We're the supportive wellness companion that helps you build a healthy relationship with food and yourself, without the shame or pressure.

Our secret? We focus on awareness, not restriction. Simply snap a photo of your meals and let AteMate AI gently guide you. There's no calorie counting, no judgment, just powerful insights into your unique habits and triggers.

Ready to find your freedom? Download AteMate today!

As seen in: Women's Health, Time Magazine, The New York Times, Forbes, The Washington Post
In Partnership with: YMCA, American Council on Exercise (ACE), US Air Force


CORE FEATURES & BENEFITS

• Photo-Based Journaling: Fast, visual, and a joy to use. Easily log meals in just 3 taps.
• Holistic Health: Connect your food, exercise, sleep, and mood on one simple timeline. Discover how your choices impact each other.
• AI-Powered Insights: Get smart, personalized insights to spot your patterns and build lasting habits, without judgment.
• AI-Food Analysis: Using the power of AI, food photos are analyzed and tagged for easier journaling
• Mindful & Intuitive Eating: This isn't a diet app. We help you rebuild body awareness and remove food judgment for an enjoyable, guilt-free life.
• Fully Customizable: Our journal adapts to you. Find what works for your unique body and journey.
• Private & Social: Keep your journal completely private, or share with friends or a coach for added support.


PRIVACY & MEMBERSHIP

Your journey is secure and ad-free.
• We do not run ads, and your personal data is never shared. 
• Your personal data is not used for AI training purposes, and we will never use your information without your consent.
• AteMate is a subscription app with a 7-day FREE trial for new users.
• This gives you full, unlimited access to the entire app—no hidden fees, gated features, or ads.
• The subscription enables us to continuously provide new features and maintain a private, secure environment for you to journal in.

FOR HEALTH COACHES
AteMate Coach is built specifically for coaches, based on feedback from coaches. 
More at atemate.com/coach


MEMBERSHIP MANAGED BY APPLE

Subscriptions are processed and managed securely by Apple. Your credit card will be charged through your Apple App Store account after your 7-day FREE trial ends. Subscriptions renew automatically unless canceled at least 24 hours before the end of the term. You can manage and cancel your subscription anytime in your App Store Account Settings after purchase.For full details, please refer to our Terms of Use and Privacy Policy, linked below.
https://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/dev/stdeu

We're excited to introduce a new chapter in our app's life with a brand that better reflects our core mission: to be a supportive companion on your health journey.

Here's what's new in this update:

• A New Name: We are now AteMate! Our mission remains the same—to be an easy-to-use, non-judgmental, mindfulness-focused journaling app.

• Your Weekly Path Review: We've enhanced our AI to give back to you. Your entries will now be automatically analyzed to provide a personalized Weekly Path Review, highlighting your unique patterns, celebrating your wins, and offering insights to support your goals.

• About Me Section: Personalize your app experience! You can now update your profile with your health goals, dietary preferences, and what’s holding you back. This helps us better tailor the app to your unique journey.

• New Customization Options: You now have the ability to hide tracking options from the capture menu, making your journaling even more effortless and personal.

This is just the beginning! We have many more exciting updates planned to make AteMate the most supportive food journal available.

Hope you like the changes.
The AteMate Team

apps.title: Rafeeq: Food Delivery in Qatar
apps.developer: RAFEEQ AL DARB TRADING SERVICES AND TRANSPORTATION
apps.description:
Welcome to Qatar's number one super app, Rafeeq – your ultimate gateway to seamless living in the heart of the Arabian Gulf. From food delivery that tantalizes your taste buds to a comprehensive range of groceries that fills your pantry with the finest, we've got it all covered. Our online shopping experience is designed to bring the mall to your doorstep, with an array of shops, including flower shops, pharmacies, clothing boutiques, beauty stores, and so much more.

Delicious Food Delivery
Craving your favorite restaurant's mouthwatering dishes? Look no further. With Rafeeq, you can order from renowned establishments like McDonald's, KFC, and a wide array of other favorite restaurants. We bring the culinary delights of Qatar's most beloved eateries right to your doorstep, ensuring that your cravings are satisfied with every bite.

Groceries at Your Fingertips
Say goodbye to long queues and heavy bags. Rafeeq's groceries section brings the supermarket to your screen, making it effortless to stock up on your everyday essentials. Whether it's fresh produce, pantry staples, or household items, we've got your grocery needs covered.

Seamless Online Shopping
Shopping enthusiasts, rejoice! Rafeeq's online shopping experience is a retail paradise where you can browse, select, and purchase a wide variety of products with just a few taps. Our virtual aisles are stocked with everything you need, and our secure payment options ensure a worry-free shopping journey.

All in One Single Rafeeq App
In one single Rafeeq app, you get it all, and you get it fast. Whether it's a delectable meal, your weekly groceries, or even a thoughtful gift like flowers, Rafeeq has you covered. Need to replenish your personal care products? We have perfumes and pharmacy items too. And because we understand the importance of giving back, Rafeeq even provides a platform for charitable contributions.

Rafeeq, a 100% Qatari-owned company, was born from a profound mission: to bridge the gap between you and your daily essentials, no matter where you call home in this beautiful country. We take pride in being your gateway to the Arabian Gulf's finest offerings, whether it's the delectable dishes from renowned restaurants, the essentials that stock your pantry, or a delightful shopping experience at your fingertips.
So, embrace the convenience, savor the flavor, and cherish the simplicity – because Every order is Delivered With Love.

apps.title: Tangelo - Get Food Prescribed!
apps.description:
Tangelo makes it easy to access affordable food prescriptions tailored to improve your health. As soon as you’re approved, we activate your food prescription and you can choose from healthy foods prescribed just for you!

GET PRESCRIBED HEALTHY FOOD

Our prescription process is simple and only takes a few minutes! Answer a few questions about how you eat today, and we measure the nutrient gaps in your diet that impact your health conditions. Then we write a food prescription for the foods you should be eating less of and more of to improve your health!

GET PRESCRIBED FOOD PAID FOR

We work with your health plan to get the cost of your personalized food prescription covered! More and more health plans across the country are covering the cost of prescribed healthy foods for their members. If your health plan doesn’t offer coverage, we offer a self-pay option using a nutrition incentive! And we accept SNAP-EBT!

GET PRESCRIBED FOOD DELIVERED

Once we confirm your coverage, your prescribed food is delivered directly to your doorstep! Every dish you receive is approved for your chronic health conditions by clinical nutrition experts, and we work with you to learn what dishes you like and don’t like to constantly improve the meals you can choose from each week!

MEASURE PROGRESS AND GET REPRESCRIBED

As you enjoy your prescribed foods week-after-week, we’ll check-in to measure your progress and understand how your diet quality is improving. As you keep going, you’ll get represcribed and we’ll help extend your coverage and connect you with additional benefits.

apps.title: Calorie Counter PRO MyNetDiary
apps.description:
Track calories, food, and macros with ease! MyNetDiary has a free barcode scanner, personal diet plans, and AI Meal Scan for instant logging — all in a smart, simple-to-use app. 

USERS SAY…

The best
Love this app! The best out of many food tracking apps that I have tried over the years. Love that it is free! The breakdown of the meal and daily nutrition is very informative. Try it you will love it!

LOVE LOVE LOVE THIS APP
Best app for tracking food, exercise! Consistently losing weight! I love how it shows you if you're on target for your goal. Great layout, great look, easy to use!!! I highly recommend this app if you're looking to be a healthier you!!!

Fast, intuitive, user friendly
I have tried other calorie tracking programs over the years and this app is by far the best I've come across. I highly recommend it. The free version is very good and I am now enjoying the extra functions through a paid subscription.

RECOGNIZED EXCELLENCE
• Ranked #1 in Forbes Health’s Best Weight Loss Apps of 2025.
• Rated #1 by the American Journal of Preventive Medicine.
• Praised by The New York Times as “simpler, quicker, and better-looking” than other apps.
• Featured in Today’s Dietitian, alongside WW and Noom.

DIFFERENT FROM OTHER DIET APPS
• Simple & Generous Features: Packed with free tools, no ads.
• Lightning-Fast Logging: Barcode scanner and AI Meal Scan make tracking effortless.
• Verified Food Database: Over 1.7 million items with 108 nutrients for accuracy.
• Privacy Focused: No account required.

MyNetDiary puts you in control. You can pick a diet or a meal plan, follow our registered dietitians' easy tips, and follow the app's guidance. Or, you can turn them off and simply use MyNetDiary as the best free calorie-counting app in the world.

PROVEN SUCCESS
• Active members lose an average of 1.4 lbs/week
• Over 25 million users have chosen MyNetDiary, many switched from other diet apps

A few of the free version features:
• Easy food, exercise, and water tracking.
• Daily coaching tips and meal reminders.
• Customizable dashboard for your goals.
• iOS Health integration and Apple Watch support.
• Shopping lists, nutrition articles, and how-to videos.

SPECIAL PRO APP FEATURES
• Up to 108 nutrients tracked
• Plan macros
• Full set of charts
• Timestamps
• Carb tracking

If you need more support, MyNetDiary Premium provides all the guidance and features you may need. At your fingertips, you'll find:

• Premium Diets, 600+ full-flavored Premium Recipes and Menus by RDs, including low-carb, keto, high-protein, Mediterranean, vegetarian, and more - with diet planners, guides, and feedback.
• Intermittent fasting - full-featured, with fasting timer and different protocols.
• Macros planning and cycling.
• Planning and tracking up to 108 nutrients, including omegas and aminos.
• Recipe import tool - easily load internet recipes and calculate complete nutrition.
• Integrations with top fitness trackers - Fitbit, Garmin, and Withings.
• In-depth reporting and analysis tools to improve your diet.

Subscription Terms:
The subscription period will automatically renew unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24 hours before the end of the current subscription period. To turn this function off, turn off auto-renew in your iTunes account. Renewal payments will differ depending on subscription and pricing at the time of renewal. Your iTunes account will be charged when the purchase is confirmed.

Privacy Policy: www.mynetdiary.com/privacy.html

apps.title: Ritual - Order Local Takeout
apps.description:
Ritual brings people together with the best takeout spots near their work or home neighborhoods. We connect you with those local gems, the hot new restaurants, and your favorite chains. We believe it’s those real world connections — when the barista knows your name, the chef knows just how you like your order, or being greeted like a regular from your very first visit — that make communities, and the people and places in them, thrive.

Order ahead and ditch the wait.
No more waiting in line to order, or killing time while your meal is being prepped. We’ll notify you exactly when it’s time to go pick up your food — so you get your latte, salad, taco, burrito, sushi, burger, pizza, poke or pad thai at its freshest. 

Menu options? Oh, we have them.
Breakfast, lunch, dinner and everything in between. Choose from hundreds of restaurants near you, and thousands of menu choices. Search by cuisine style or restaurant proximity. Quickly reorder your faves or discover new places. Easily customize your orders too. Whatever you’re in the mood for, find it in the App.

Be the office hero.
Doing a lunch or coffee run? Get your coworkers in on it. With Piggyback, it’s easy to create work teams and place group orders. No more counting back change, or figuring out who’s paid. Earn bonus points (from us, and with your colleagues) when you pick up, plus get in some daily steps! 10 coffees, one easy and rewarding run — epic.

Get rewarded with Loyalty+.
Got a go-to breakfast, lunch or coffee spot? Earn extra rewards for those daily rituals. With Loyalty+, you collect stamps at your favorite local participating restaurants. Redeem those stamps for free food. Repeat. It’s a delicious cycle.

Enjoy easy and secure payment.
Thousands of local spots, one quick and easy way to pay. Save your personal or company credit card in the app, and pay with a tap. Your data is encrypted, so we or the restaurant never see your number. And your card or cash stays in your wallet, for safe, contact-free payments and pick ups.

Reward employees with Ritual for Companies.
Our corporate teams program makes it easy to reward employees through credits, meal plans, and other perks. Create employee meal plans that work with your team’s size & budget, and support favorite local merchants through targeted incentives. Our user-friendly portal makes office ordering quick and easy, whether your team is 10 or 100+.

raw_data.releaseNotes:
Some improvements under the hood to support our partners and users. Be on the lookout for new and exciting things coming soon!

Happy eating, friends!

apps.title: FreshGoGo Asian Grocery & Food
apps.description: FreshGoGo is an Asian online grocery and authentic Asian food shopping and delivery service in North America supported by advanced technical platform. FreshGoGo provides customers with fresh and high-quality of Fresh Vegetables, Poultry & Meat, Fish & Seafood, Pantry, Dry Goods, Frozen Items, Refrigerated Items, Snacks, Drinks, as well as gourmet Asian food from local famous stores and restaurants at competitive prices. FreshGoGo customers can not only choose grocery items and process an order through multiple devices (smart phone, tablet and PC), but also track the order/delivery status in real time from the point of order creation to the delivery, such as exact time when the order is loaded to the truck and when the order arrives. FreshGoGo offers home delivery service, to nearby pickup locations and UPS/FedEx shipping to all states. FreshGoGo makes grocery and food shopping & delivery fast and easy.

apps.title: ChowNow: Local Food Ordering
apps.description:
We’re not your usual ordering app. We don’t believe in crazy-high commissions for independent restaurants, to start. Or marked-up menu prices for you. But we still have delivery and takeout from the best local restaurants–so dig in.

EXPLORE NEARBY RESTAURANTS
Search for local takeout, delivery, or curbside pickup options by cuisine, restaurant name, deals and more. Maybe you’re looking for a specific type of food? Here’s a taste of what you could find on our app: Italian, Vietnamese, Korean, Japanese, Mexican, Thai, Greek, Chinese, French, Mediterranean, Indian, and a lot more. Check out our map to find places that are open right now, or offering a promotion. Order what you want by customizing menu items, and get it delivered with convenient, real-time tracking updates. 

CHECK OUT FAST
Enable Apple Pay or save your card info for easy payment and fast checkout. Plus, quick reordering options help you get your favorites again in a snap.

GET HELP FROM REAL HUMANS
We’re here 24/7. Reach out to our team via chat, SMS, phone, or email. We’re here around the clock if you need help—or just want to talk food.

WE’RE OPEN NEAR YOU
We’ll help you find the best restaurants at most U.S. locations. Order fresh flavors in Los Angeles, New York, Chicago, San Francisco, Washington DC, Boston, Atlanta, Denver, Portland, Seattle, Philadelphia, Brooklyn, Dallas, Austin, Orange County, San Diego, Cleveland, Minneapolis, and Charlotte.

STILL READING?
We like your style. How about pizza delivery, pasta, burritos, barbecue, sushi, salads, vegetarian, vegan, burgers and fries? 

We even have desserts, coffee, smoothies—you name it. So go for it. Download the app and grab something good. We’re here if you need help.

apps.title: Samsung Food: Meal Planner
apps.description:
Samsung Food — The Most Powerful Free Meal Planning App

What if your meal planner could do it all — for free?

Samsung Food brings you everything you need to plan meals, save recipes, shop smarter, and cook better. All in one place.

We help millions of home cooks — from beginners to pros — eat healthier, save time, reduce food waste, and enjoy cooking more.

With Samsung Food, you can:

• Discover over 240,000 public recipes, including 124,000 fully guided ones.
• Search recipes by ingredients — from over 42,000 recognized products in 26 languages — or filter by meal type, cook time, cuisine, or 14 different diets.
• Save any recipe from any website and make it your own.
• Plan your weekly meals, turn them into smart shopping lists, and share them with friends or family.
• Organize family shopping with shared grocery lists.
• Get groceries delivered from one of our 23 integrated retailers across 4 regions.
• Explore 192,000 community notes and tips shared by real cooks.
• Join over 5,400 public food communities with 4.5 million members — including Jamie Oliver!
• Access detailed nutrition information and health scores on over 218,500 recipes.

All this, available for free on your iPhone, iPad, or web.

Want even more? Samsung Food+ unlocks advanced features:

• AI-personalized weekly meal plans tailored to your health goals.
• Smart recipe customization — adjust servings, swap ingredients, or tweak nutrition.
• Step-by-step Smart Cooking Mode for any recipe.
• Automated pantry management with personalized cooking suggestions.
• Nutrition tracking with adaptive meal plans to help you meet your goals.
• Save and reuse unlimited meal plans anytime.

Plus, connect seamlessly with Samsung SmartThings Cooking for a smarter kitchen experience. Try Samsung Food+ for even more ways to eat well — your way.

Download Samsung Food today and take the hassle out of meal planning, shopping, and cooking.

Questions? Contact us at support@samsungfood.com

Terms of Use: samsungfood.com/policy/terms/

advisories: Infrequent/Mild Alcohol, Tobacco, or Drug Use or References
raw_data.releaseNotes:
This update brings a meaningful change to how tailored meal plans work - and a small but important fix to Recipe Builder.

- Tailored plans are now available to all users: apply a full week plan up to 2 times for free (subscription required if you want more)
- We removed the "Try Next" section from the Home screen to keep things simpler
- Fixed an issue in Recipe Builder where recipes couldn't be saved if they contained unrecognized ingredients - you'll now see a warning but can still save

Meet Careem – the everything app for your everyday needs.


From dining at your favorite restaurants and cafes to groceries, rides, and more, Careem has your back.
Whether you need to EAT, GET, or GO, it’s all just a tap away.


Go anywhere with ease with Careem Rides 
Getting from A to B shouldn’t be a trauma. With Careem, you can book a ride in seconds or schedule a pick-up and drop-off for later. There’s always an option for every budget and mood. 


Explore the culinary scene with Careem DineOut 
Craving a delightful coffee, a hearty brunch, or a sumptuous dinner? With Careem DineOut, you can enjoy up to 50% off at a curated selection of top cafes and restaurants across Riyadh. Whether you're seeking a cozy café ambiance or a vibrant dining experience, Careem DineOut connects you to the best spots in the city. No vouchers, no hassle—just effortless dining and great discounts. Savor delicious meals today!


Get premium groceries delivered fast with Careem Market by Tamimi 
Get your groceries delivered in just 20 minutes with Careem Market by Tamimi! Enjoy the trusted quality of Tamimi Markets, now with the convenience and speed of Careem. Whether you want to stock up for the week, restock your fridge mid-week, craving a snack or get your hands on a viral trend, Careem Market by Tamimi has you covered. Get your groceries delivered in 20 minutes — no stress, no hassle.
From fresh milk, eggs, and bread to your favorite snacks, Careem brings you everything you need, exactly when you need it. Enjoy quality you trust at prices you'll love.
With over 7,000+ items available, Careem Market by Tamimi makes grocery shopping effortless. Experience a smooth, easy-to-use app and high-quality groceries delivered straight to your door.

* Top‑quality fresh fruits & vegetables
* Daily staples: milk, bread, butter, eggs, cheese
* Your favorite snacks, biscuits, chips, ice cream & chocolates
* Rice, lentils, cooking oil & spices
* Personal care essentials, cleaning & laundry supplies


Get your home cleaned with HomeCleaning powered by JustLife 
Thought we only offered rides and deliveries? Careem now offers even more ways to make your life easier - book home cleaning services with a few taps, all from the app. Whatever you want or need, Careem is here to deliver it fast and conveniently.


Explore Madinah in a fun and eco-friendly way with Careem Bike & Scooters 
Want to beat traffic and discover the city? Hop on an electric Careem Bike or Scooter and cruise through Madinah's vibrant streets. With nearly 1,000  bikes and scooters across the city, you can easily find a bike or scooter near you. Ride tracking ensures you always know where you're headed, and with instant booking, you're on your way without delay. Currently, Careem Bike is available exclusively in Madinah. Stay tuned as we plan to expand this service to more cities across Saudi Arabia in the near future.


Your all-in-one App for Everyday Needs 
Whether it's rides, groceries, dining, or more, Careem brings everything you need to your fingertips. With just a tap, access a world of services designed to make your life easier.


Exclusive Deals for New Users 
First time with Careem? Enjoy special welcome offers and discounts tailored just for you. Start saving from your very first ride, groceries order, or HomeCleaning booking.


Exclusive Deals for Careem Plus Members 
15% cash back on Rides, free delivery & member-exclusive deals on groceries await our most loyal customers. 


Reliable and Timely Service
Experience our supercharged delivery network, ensuring your orders arrive exactly when you expect them - no delays, no hassle.


Download Careem Today
Take back your time and enjoy the convenience of having everything you need in one app. Because with Careem, you've got better things to do.

apps.title: The Chefz: Fast Food Delivery
apps.description:
The Chefz is the best food delivery application where you can enjoy your day. With chefz you can order from a variety of stores that include Elite restaurants, upper casual and casual restaurants, sweets, drinks, bakeries, coffee, flowers, and even perfumes delivered to your door in time.
 
If you are thinking about your favorite food for dinner, a cake for your special occasion, or flowers? Then The Chefz app is your only choice.
You can find your favorite restaurants Or, get exactly what you are craving by searching for a specific restaurant, or cuisine. Pizza. Burgers. Sushi. Pasta. Shawarma
We happily serve you in Riyadh, Eastern province, Jeddah

The Chefz app is the main exclusive sponsor of restaurants reservations in Riyadh season. We’ve created a customized UI for Riyadh season’s reservations including all zones that’s covered.
 
The chefz is a special Application for  food delivery 

• Fast delivery 
• Browse Dishes details
• Whether you need your food now or schedule it for later
• Track your Order
• View previous reviews and ratings
• Find exclusive deals from the ‘offers’ section  or Free Delivery Section that gives you access to top discounts
• Pay the way you prefer( visa, Mada, Cash on delivery, Apple pay, MasterCard).
• Send Gifts (perfumes, flower, Cake, chocolate box)

 
 
 
ذا شفز أفضل تطبيق لتوصيل ألذ خيارات الطعام، استمتع بيومك مع ذا شفز بإمكانك الطلب من متاجر مختلفة تتضمن أرقى صناع الطعام الفاخر، مطاعم متنوعة و مميزة ،  ألذ الحلويات و المخبوزات وايضاً الورود والعطور  تصل الى باب منزلك في الوقت المحدد 
 
ذا شفز هو خيارك الوحيد لأكلتك المفضلة او كيكة لمناسباتك المميزة أو حتى ورود  
في ذا شفز ستجد مطعمك المفضل والحصول على ما تريده بالبحث من خلال تصنيف معين مثل: الإيطالي برجر، اسيوي، شاورما والكثير من الخيارات   
 سعيدين بخدمتكم في الرياض، المنطقة الشرقية، جدة  
ذا شفز تطبيق مميز وخيارك الأول لتطبيق توصيل الطعام
 ذا شفز هو الشريك الرسمي لحجوزات مطاعم موسم الرياض 



• أسرع تطبيق توصيل طعام
• سهولة تصفح معلومات الأطباق
• إذا كنت بحاجة إلى طعامك الآن أو جدولته لوقت لاحق
• يمكنك تتبع طلبك
• معاينة التعليقات والتقييم من عملاء سابقين
• ستجد أفضل خيارات العروض الحصرية من قسم "العروض" أو قسم التوصيل المجاني 
• ادفع بالطريقة التي تفضلها (فيزا، مدى، نقدًا عند الاستلام، أبل باي، ماستركارد).
• يمكنك بسهولة إرسال هدايا (عطور، ورد، كيك، علبة شوكولاتة)

raw_data.releaseNotes:
We work hard to provide a better and easier ordering experience, and this update contains several bug fixes.

apps.title: Cookpad Recipes, homemade food
apps.description:
Transform your everyday ingredients and cook delicious meals with Cookpad! Designed for home cooks of all skill levels, Cookpad offers step by step easy-to-follow, flavorful recipes. Explore a vast collection of recipes, save your favorites, and use Cookpad as your personal recipe organizer with themed folders. Share your own creations and discover new dishes from a vibrant food-loving community. Download Cookpad today and start cooking!

MAIN FATURES:

Endless inspiration, thousands of recipes for your everyday meals: 
- From tasty & healthy breakfasts to quick lunches and mouth-watering dinners, explore thousands of home-cooked recipes. And don’t forget the desserts—baked, frozen, or made in an air fryer!
- Global flavors: Discover dishes from Spanish, Italian, Thai, Japanese, and other cuisines 
- Ingredient-based search: Cook great meals with what you already have in your fridge or pantry. Save money, reduce food waste, and make cooking more enjoyable.
- Catering to all diets: Use filters to find recipes for specific preferences like vegan, vegetarian, keto, gluten-free, and more
- Healthy and diverse cooking methods: From roasting and grilling to using an air fryer, Instant Pot, or slow cooker, find a variety of methods in one powerful app 

Keep all your recipes organized in one sole place:
- Build your personal collection of recipes and keep all your cooking adventures organized
- Create private folders by category (such as fish or meat recipes, desserts, etc.) and plan your weekly menus effortlessly

Share your cooking creations:
- Share your favorite recipes with friends, family, or the Cookpad community
- Or keep your creations private, just for you

Join a vibrant community:
- Connect with passionate home cooks, follow other food creators, and get help in the kitchen when you need it
- Upload photos (cooksnaps) of the dishes you’ve cooked and share your cooking experience with others.
- Cookpad is designed for everyone—from beginners to experienced cooks—and for any occasion, from daily meals to special gatherings. 

Cookpad app is ads-free
- Enjoy a seamless free from interruption cooking experience with Cookpad app!

Cookpad is free to download and use. For those looking to enhance their experience, we offer an optional subscription service with the following features:
- Get the most popular recipes at the top of search results with Premium Search.
- Save unlimited recipes from other home cooks, so you always have inspiration at hand.
- Use advanced search filters to match your cooking preferences.

Cookpad Premium is available in Arabic speaking countries, Argentina, Brazil, Chile, Colombia, France, Greece, Hungary, India (English only), Indonesia, Italy, Malaysia, Mexico, Romania, Poland, Spain, Taiwan, Thailand, Ukraine, United Kingdom, United States, Uruguay and Vietnam.

Terms & Conditions: 
- Your monthly payment will be charged to your Apple ID account 
- Your subscription is automatically renewed month by month, unless you cancel it with a minimum of 24 hours before the end of the current period 
- Your account will be renewed in the 24 hours before the end of the current period
- Unless stated otherwise at the point of subscription, the monthly renewal cost is the same as the initial cost. 
- Subscriptions are managed by you and auto-renewal of the Premium Service can be canceled by going to your Apple ID account settings after purchase. 
- Read the full Terms & Conditions here. https://cookpad.com/en/terms 
- Read the privacy policy here: https://cookpad.com/en/privacy Get in touch with us: help@cookpad.com

Contact us with any feedback or suggestions: help@cookpad.com

raw_data.releaseNotes:
We've polished a few things behind the scenes—bug fixes and UI improvements—to keep your cooking experience smooth and enjoyable.

Cookpad is constantly improving the app. Update now to enjoy the latest features and fixes.
We welcome your feedback via "Menu > Send Feedback" in the app!

Healthy Food Recipes delivers a box of delicious recipes and the exact amount of fresh ingredients you need to cook them at home
In our App you will find:
• Thousands of delicious recipes that you can discover, sort, save to your favorites, rank, and share with your friends and family.
• Amazing recipes for you that are easy to prepare. Our meals are interesting yet simple. And we ensure that your diet is balanced and varied.
• Step-by-step guides to help you cook your meals. 
• Explore new recipe and articles recommended just for you daily.
Get cooking, eat well, and be healthy! 

Renewing and Cancellation

Subscription with a free trial period will automatically renew to a paid subscription unless auto-renewal is turn off. Payment will be charged to your iTunes Account at confirmation of purchase. Subscription automatically renews unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24-hours before the end of the current period. Account will be charged for renewal within 24-hour prior to the end of the current period. The cost of the renewal will match the initial subscription price. Your auto-renew subscription can be managed or turned off by going to your Account Settings after purchase. No cancellation of the current subscription is allowed during your active subscription period. Any unused portion of a free trial period, if offered, will be forfeited when purchasing a subscription during the free trial period. If your subscription expires – you will need to purchase a new subscription to access all premium features.

apps.title: Food City Mobile
apps.description:
Welcome to the Food City App!

The Food City app offers a smooth, fast, and intuitive experience, making your grocery shopping journey easier than ever. With a fresh, clean look, all favorite features are here, like digital coupons, weekly ads, shopping lists, plus curbside pickup and delivery options to fit your busy lifestyle. Explore personalized recipe suggestions based on your favorite ingredients, and add them directly to your shopping list or cart for a seamless experience.

Features:

Weekly Ads

Explore the latest savings with our clickable weekly ads. Easily shop special deals and everyday values in one place. Choose to view the ad by list or print format for added convenience.

Digital Coupons

Save time and money with Digital Coupons. Simply click to add them to your ValuCard, and redeem them instantly at checkout with qualifying purchases. Filter and sort coupons to match your preferences.

Shopping Lists

Keep your grocery shopping organized with our mobile shopping lists. Use the built-in barcode scanner to quickly add items, and navigate the store with ease as the app sorts your list by aisle.

Barcode Scan

Our improved Barcode Scan feature lets you instantly add products to your list or cart by scanning them. Discover relevant digital coupons, offers, and nutritional facts with just a scan.

My Favorites & Past Purchases

Quickly build your order by browsing your favorite products and viewing past purchases. This streamlined feature allows you to toggle between favorites and previous buys, making in-store and curbside shopping faster and more convenient.

In-Store Shopping Experience

Optimize your in-store experience with our enhanced shopping list features. Sort your list by aisle, easily swipe off items as you shop, and discover associated coupons and offers as you go.

Pick-up Time Slot Reservations

Plan ahead with our Timeslot reservation feature for Curbside Pickup. Your reserved pickup time is displayed from the moment you start shopping, ensuring a smooth and timely experience.

Meal Planner

Plan meals effortlessly with our Meal Planner. Choose from a wide range of recipes and create meal plans for up to seven days. Perfect for holidays, special events, or dietary needs, meal planning has never been easier.

ValuCard

No more carrying extra cards! Your digital ValuCard is always at your fingertips. Scan it at the register right from your phone and track your Fuel Bucks balance easily within the app.

ABOUT FOOD CITY

Shop your local Food City for fresh, high-quality products at competitive prices. Let us make grocery shopping convenient with our Curbside Pickup and Delivery services.

How Does Curbside Pickup Work?

Shop anytime from anywhere with all the conveniences of in-store shopping, including special offers, digital coupons, and ValuCard rewards. Use the Past Purchases option to quickly reorder your favorites. Our Curbside Shoppers select items based on your preferences, ensuring you get the best quality. Pay online or at pickup, with no minimum order required. Enjoy same-day pickup in as little as three hours without leaving your vehicle — we’ll load your order directly into your car.

Is Pickup Available Near You?

Easily check for participating Curbside Pickup locations by entering your zip code in the app.

Discover the new Food City app today and experience grocery shopping made faster, easier, and more convenient!

advisories: Frequent/Intense Alcohol, Tobacco, or Drug Use or References

Shop anytime from anywhere with all the conveniences of in-store shopping, including special offers, digital coupons, and ValuCard rewards. Use the Past Purchases option to quickly reorder your favorites. Our Curbside Shoppers select items based on your preferences, ensuring you get the best quality. Pay online or at pickup, with no minimum order required. Enjoy same-day pickup in as little as three hours without leaving your vehicle — we’ll load your order directly into your car.

Is Pickup Available Near You?

Easily check for participating Curbside Pickup locations by entering your zip code in the app.

Discover the new Food City app today and experience grocery shopping made faster, easier, and more convenient!

apps.title: FitGenie: Macro & Food Tracker
apps.description:
Don’t spend another Sunday in the kitchen meal prepping when you could be enjoying your life (or your couch, no judgments). 

FitGenie lets you get healthy, local, chef-prepped meals delivered whenever you want them, then makes it oh-so-easy to make sure those meals help you reach your goals with FREE macro tracking & personalized nutrition plans. 

We’re committed to giving our customers easy access to the best local meal delivery services and data-backed, customizable nutrition plans to make sure those meals work for you. 


Do you serve my area? 

We’re an Atlanta-based company and currently serving our neighbors and working with the best healthy meal delivery services in our area. But keep an eye out because we’ll be expanding our options.


Do I have to subscribe to anything? 

Nope, you can get meals delivered whenever you want them. No subscription required. 


Do I have to track my food? 

You don’t have to use the food log to get meals delivered (but all the research seems to tell us that tracking food intake is one of the most effective ways to lose weight/gain muscle/change your body if that’s what you’re into). 


What happens when I reach my goal? 

You’ll be prompted to check-in weekly and our AI dietician will help you adjust your food plan to keep you on track. 


Ready to reclaim your weekends from meal prep? 

Download the app.


———

1 Month
6 Months
12 Months

Integrations:

Learn more at:
