apps.title: World Chef
apps.description:
Do you like exotic food? Are you more of a burger and fries kind of person? Either way, there's a spot for you in the kitchens of World Chef, the most international cooking game, with chefs and recipes from over 20 nationalities!

World Chef is a happy place where the kitchen never closes, the waiter always has a big smile on his face and the food is so great you should probably play with a bib on.

Open your restaurant, give it a name and decorate it to your taste! Then start cooking world cuisines and serving customers! Your place will soon become so popular you'll have to make it bigger!

Expand your menu with every new international chef: Tacos, pizza, sushi,... The whole world can fit inside one restaurant! The success ladder will lead you to welcoming VIP diners and even catering special events! You will soon master the art of running a top restaurant.

And remember! This is not a fast food joint, take your time to slow-cook your best recipes. Your customers know they will be worth the waiting.

----

FEATURES:
* Create, decorate and run your own fine dining restaurant!
* Craft exclusive decorations at the Design Studio.
* Buy and trade fresh ingredients and cook increasingly delicious dishes.
* Build yourself a dock, get a boat and start importing exotic ingredients!
* Serve your finest cuisine to customers from all around the world.
* Increase your popularity and see how all the VIPs become regulars!

----

World Chef is FREE to download and FREE to play. However, you can purchase in-app items for the game with real money. If you wish to disable this feature, please turn off the in-app purchases in your phone or tablet's Settings.

Do Not Sell My Personal Information: https://www.take2games.com/ccpa/

advisories: Infrequent/Mild Alcohol, Tobacco, or Drug Use or References

Smiles is e&'s full-service lifestyle SuperApp and one of the largest one-stop shops for the everyday needs of UAE residents and visitors. With 6,500 participating brands and over 15,000 partner outlets in the UAE, Smiles offers deals and rewards on food and grocery deliveries, home services booking, e& services as well as dining, shopping, entertainment, wellness and travel benefits, making it a premier lifestyle SuperApp.



Earn and redeem Smiles points on all transactions on food, grocery, home services, shopping, travel & more.



Looking for delicious food delivered to your doorstep? We've got you covered! Browse through our extensive selection of 12,000 plus restaurants to order your favorite dishes.

انضم إلى حلقة من التوفير بلا حدود مع Smiles Unlimited. احصل على توصيل مجاني على طلبات الأكل والبقالة، وبدون رسوم خدمة على حجز الخدمات المنزلية وعروض اشترِ 1 واحصل على 1 مجاناً بلا حدود.

apps.title: Savor Food
apps.description:
Share what you savor. Because friends don't let friends order badly.

Savor is a visual, dish-based, review app that enables you to quickly post, rate, and share what you savor most when dining out.

Unlike venue-based restaurant review apps, Savor tells you where to go AND what to order when you get there.

Features:

• A constantly streaming “Feed” of the latest posts by Savor users in your area.
• An innovative "Foodie Alerts” feature that alerts you when you're near a favorite place or highly-rated favorite menu item.
• Runs natively on the Apple Watch.
• An "Explore" tab to see the highest rated menu items around you with one simple tap.
• Real-time notifications when someone likes, comments, mentions, or follows you.
• Easily share Savor posts via other social networks including Facebook, Pinterest, Twitter, and Instagram.
• Integration with Uber's ride-sharing service.

Become a Savor ambassador for your community by posting about your favorite dishes and drinks when dining out.

apps.title: Tastebuddy - Buy Homemade Food
apps.description:
Tastebuddy - Bringing tasty, local homemade food from around the world to your home!


Main Features:

Are you a foodie or just hungry? 
- Order tasty homemade food from local restaurants and home cooks & chefs.
- Follow your favorite chefs and restaurants.
- Easy and convenient to use: Find everything  in one place!


How many people have wasted hours trying to find a place that makes a specialty cookie for special occasions, or those homemade tamales? 


Tastebuddy is a connection tool that brings all things food together so that foodies can find exactly what they need and what they’re looking for, and a tool for home chefs, local restaurants and community markets to sell and market their products in one place, from anywhere, at any time. Our mission is to provide a better way for people to get their passion for food known throughout the world in a cost effective way, and to give foodies a consistent way to search and discover what they love, all in one place.


Now, those that have a passion for food and want to showcase their authentic or unique flavors can have a platform to help them succeed.


Create a digital Restaurant or Shop - 
With all things digital in this world, Tastebuddy fills one of the major gaps in the food industry which is the ability for people to search for, sell and market their homemade food online and in one place.


Support Local - 
Tastebuddy supports the local cooks and suppliers and helps them share, sell and/or expand their business in an easy and cost effective way.


Easy & Convenient - 
Everything food is now seamless and in one location. Tastebuddy streamlines the process of buying and selling food.

Customize your Business and your Search - 
Sellers customize their business and how they want it to run and operate and shoppers customize their search to finally find exactly what they want.


For any questions, please feel free to contact us at info@tastebuddyfoods.com.

apps.title: Healthi: Weight Loss, Diet App
apps.description:
Lose weight the Healthi way!
◆◆◆◆◆ - "Love it and have lost 20lbs already!"
◆◆◆◆◆ - "Easy to track BITES and stay on track!"
◆◆◆◆◆ - "Great app love it! Use it constantly!"

Studies show that 88% of people who track their food consistently, see weight loss results in just 7 days! 
Staying on track and logging your daily eating habits couldn’t be easier than with Healthi. Simply scan the barcode or search your food in our food database to find out how many BITES / Calories / Macros / Net Carbs your meal is. You can even favorite the foods you eat most often and use the Recipe Builder to create all your favorite meals.

But diet and weight loss isn't just about tracking numbers. That's why we've created a community of like-minded individuals who will cheer you on and provide the support you need to succeed. You can connect with other users, talk with Healthi Coaches, attend Member Meetings, share your progress, and get inspired by success stories from people just like you.

With 6 personalized plans, the EASIEST to use tracking features, and a SUPPORTIVE community, you'll have everything you need to reach your goals and transform your health.

** NEW … INTRODUCING **
HealthiCare
GLP-1 + Healthi
Achieve lasting, healthy weight loss with HealthiCare, the ultimate combination of GLP-1 medication and Healthi’s proven weight loss ecosystem. Experience the power of Medication + Care — and see real, lasting and healthy results.
HealthiCare GLP-1 treatments include; Compounded Semaglutide, Compounded Tirzepatide, Ozempic, Wegovy and Mounjaro.

Losing Weight is EASY with Healthi, achieve real Weight Loss in 3 SIMPLE STEPS => 
 
> STEP 1: Select Your Weight Loss Plan: -> Answer a few simple questions about yourself, your cravings and your habits, and get a personalized weight loss plan catered to helping you achieve your weight loss goals in a sustainable way.
 
> STEP 2: Track What You Eat: -> the Healthi app is the EASIEST app to track your food with. Scan Barcodes, search Restaurant Menus, browse +100,000 Recipes, Explore Meal Plans, and access millions of foods.

> STEP 3: Find Support with the Community: -> Share your progress, ask questions, and get inspired by others who are on their own weight loss journey. Our large and vibrant community is here to support you every step of the way. 

Check out our amazing Healthi app features:
- 6 unique weight loss plans, 1 is perfect for you
- Track BITES, calories, and macros at the same time on one simple dashboard
- Discover an intuitive, simplified food search experience that makes tracking easier than ever
- Barcode scanner for over 1 million products
- +100,000+ Recipes (Pro)
- Easily create & share recipes (Pro)
- Restaurant database with millions of foods and restaurant items (Pro)
- Fitbit, Apple Watch and Apple HealthKit Integration (Pro)
- Explore Meal Plans from Coaches, Members and our Community (Pro)
- Voice Tracking (Pro)
- An authentic community where you can find support and inspiration from other users
- Easy-to-use weight tracker with Milestone Achievement Badges to celebrate your progress!
- Specialized weight loss and meal plans for Keto
- Works for all Food Score based systems as well as Calories and Net Carbs
- Check out the screenshots & see for yourself

Download Healthi today and use your phone to kickstart your journey toward better health. 
 
*** iTrackBites is now Healthi ***

Premium Subscription
Healthi is free to download & use. If you choose to upgrade to Healthi PRO you'll be billed $59.99 annually, charged to your iTunes Account, which will automatically renew unless canceled at least 24 hours before the end of the current period. Auto-renew can be turned off anytime by going to your Account Settings in iTunes after purchase. No cancellation of the current subscription is allowed during active subscription period.
 
Contact us for help: ios-support@Healthiapp.com

apps.title: Barakah | Fresh Food, Saved
apps.developer: Istidamat Albarakah Information Technology Company, LLC
apps.description:
Save Meals. Enjoy Deals. Share the Barakah

Barakah connects you with surplus meals from top restaurants, cafés, and bakeries — fresh, delicious, and up to 70% off every day!

Why You’ll Love Barakah
- Discover great meals for less.
- Follow your favorite spots and get instant updates on surplus meals nearby.
- Explore Member Experiences—see what others got, share your finds, and discover hidden gems from the Barakah community.
- Send a Gift Voucher—share blessings with friends and family, and let them enjoy a meal full of Barakah. 
- Pay easily with Apple Pay, Mada, or credit card.

How It Works
Restaurants and cafés sometimes end their day with perfectly fresh meals that just didn’t sell.
Barakah gives these meals a second chance—offering them to you at up to 70% off.
You save money, reduce waste, and enjoy good food that deserves to be shared.


Available in all major cities in KSA. 
Want to see us in your city? Follow us on social media and send us a direct message of where you would like us to come next!

Don't miss out on our 100% fresh deals! Download the app now and enjoy blessings in every bite.


Follow us for sustainability tips, new restaurants, exclusive offers, and community stories!

Instagram - @barakahapp
Twitter - @barakahapp
TikTok - @barakahapp

apps.title: Cooking Craze: Restaurant Game
apps.description:
Cook up a storm serving food from around the world playing our free restaurant game Cooking Craze. Prepare, cook & serve tasty dishes like a professional chef and master the kitchen as you tap to grill, bake and cook your way to the top.

Bake wood-fired pizza in Rome, grill juicy burgers in New York and prepare fine French cuisine in Paris — but be careful, playing fast isn’t enough! You need to keep your customers happy in order to grow your empire. Can you take the heat, Chef?

Cook classic restaurant dishes from across the globe;
• Make hundreds of delicious dishes including burgers, pizza, sushi, ramen, dumplings and more
• Grill fresh fish, tasty steak, succulent shrimp, and veggie kabobs
• Love desserts? Why not deep fry sweet donuts, bake baklava, serve ice cream, cheesecake or cakes?

Create a Restaurant Empire!
• Choose from over 100 ingredients cooking up tasty cuisine
• Create premium dishes with delicious new ingredients
• Launch new restaurants while learning new cooking techniques
• Add a new recipe from each city you visit
• Cook in a variety of settings

Level up with Cooking Quests, Powerful Boosts and features!
• Serve food fast while managing your time to earn kitchen upgrades
• Beat over 4000 levels across six continents
• Master all 3 difficulty levels to get golden comment cards to earn free coins and spoons
• Dash through service to earn BIG TIPS or work extra shifts to earn money for upgrades
• Equip your chef with treats for customers, non-stick pans and MORE!
• Upgrade your kitchen & increase your speed
• Use a variety of special boosts to cook your way to victory
• Cook GREEN with an Eco Boost & go organic for more tips
• Win achievements by completing combos, cooking perfect meals & earning big tips

The best restaurant gaming experience:
• New levels and cities around the world added regularly
• Hours of free fun, whenever, wherever you want!
• Play online or OFFLINE WITHOUT WIFI or internet after initial download!
Download Cooking Craze and create your own kitchen empire!

apps.title: Goldbelly: Ship Food & Gifts
apps.description:
Goldbelly is America’s #1 food marketplace. We make it possible to experience America’s most loved foods shipped right to your door. From curated meal kits from legendary chefs and signature dishes from renowned restaurants, to iconic regional specialties and gorgeous food gifts, Goldbelly connects you with magical food experiences — no matter where you are.   

Goldbelly was named one of Fast Company’s “World’s Most Innovative Companies” and Time Magazine’s “Top 50 Websites” and has been featured in The New York Times, The Wall Street Journal, CNBC and Forbes. 

DISCOVER EXTRAORDINARY FOOD EXPERIENCES 
With a selection of over 10,000 products from across all 50 states, discover and enjoy new culinary experiences from around the country—whatever you dream of, wherever you are.    

ORDER AMERICA’S MOST LOVED FOODS 
From iconic regional delicacies to local mom & pop shops, order famous eats from America’s top food makers shipped anywhere nationwide.   
 
GIFT DELICIOUSLY  
From nostalgic hometown favorites to show-stopping artisanal desserts, find beautifully packaged, delicious food gifts from some of the world’s top food brands and restaurants. 

EAT WHAT YOU WATCH  
Watch videos from America’s top chefs, streaming only on Goldbelly TV—and then shop your favorite foods on the first video network that lets you eat what you watch.

apps.title: mySymptoms Food Diary
apps.description:
Explore the connection between your diet and health with mySymptoms. Easily track your meals, symptoms, and share detailed journals with your clinicians. Our sophisticated analysis uncovers patterns and relationships between your dietary habits and symptoms, empowering you with the insights needed to manage and improve your digestive health and well-being.

Try mySymptoms free for 7 days. The app is subscription-based and includes food and symptom tracking, plus analysis to uncover patterns that support your health journey.

Featured in ‘The Best Gut Health Apps’ by Healthline. Join over 800,000 people who use mySymptoms for their IBS, IBD, low FODMAP diet, migraines, eczema, and more.

“This app is simply the best in terms of keeping track of your foods and symptoms. In addition to medication and exercise. It is helping me a lot to keep a journal to track my SIBO and IBS.” [mySymptoms customer]


DIARY / JOURNAL

• Food & health tracking: Log all aspects of your health, including food, drink, medication, stress, exercise, and environmental factors.
• Food database: Search or scan barcodes to access our extensive database of foods.
• Symptom tracking: Log symptom intensity, duration, and additional notes.
• Wellness Metrics: Log your energy, sleep quality, and bowel movements (using Bristol scale)
• Customization: Add your own drinks, foods, meals, medications, exercises, and symptoms.


INSIGHTS & ANALYSIS

• Correlation analysis: Explore how different foods affect your symptoms, helping you identify potential triggers and patterns.
• Detailed reports: Featuring specific metrics, histograms, and trend charts that visually illustrate trends over time.
• Event review: A detailed list of instances where specific foods or symptoms occurred.


SHARING & REPORTS

• Share with your clinician: Securely share your diary with your clinician through our dedicated Clinic web app.
• Family access: Share access on multiple devices using the same account.
• Data export: Export your food diary for review or sharing with health professionals in PDF or CSV formats.


PRIVACY & SECURITY

• Privacy first: Your account starts with an anonymous username ensuring confidentiality. Your name and email are only required if you choose to share your diary with a clinician.
• Robust security: Your data is fully encrypted both during transmission and while stored in the cloud.
• Control your data: We never share or sell your personal data. You may choose to participate in optional studies that help advance health research.
• HIPAA & GDPR compliant: Share your diary with clinicians confidently, knowing our app meets HIPAA & GDPR (Health Data) standards for protecting sensitive patient information. 


mySymptoms is used by individuals managing conditions such as:

• IBS (Irritable Bowel Syndrome)
• IBD (Inflammatory Bowel Disease)
• Food intolerance and sensitivities such as dairy, gluten, lactose
• Acid reflux
• Crohn’s disease
• Celiac disease
• SIBO (Small Intestinal Bacterial Overgrowth)
• Ulcerative colitis
• Migraines & cluster headaches
• Eczema
• Bloating, heartburn, and many other digestive conditions 

Try mySymptoms and start your journey to improved digestive health and well-being today!


SUBSCRIPTION INFO

mySymptoms provides a subscription service with a free trial. Cancel anytime during the trial without fees. After the trial, you’re billed monthly, semi-annually, or annually based on your plan.

Manage or cancel your subscription anytime through your App Store subscriptions. Ensure changes are made 24 hours before renewal to prevent charges.


TERMS & CONDITIONS

Terms of Use: https://www.mysymptoms.net/terms
Privacy policy: https://www.mysymptoms.net/privacy


MEDICAL DISCLAIMER

mySymptoms, a wellness tool, tracks diet and health patterns to support, not replace, healthcare relationships; not for medical diagnosis.

raw_data.releaseNotes:
User interface fixes for compatibility with recent iOS changes. Thank you for your support!

Have a symptom-free day!

apps.title: Food Truck Chef™: Cooking Game
apps.description:
Become a World-Famous Food Truck Chef!

Travel the globe with Victoria, Flo & Emily in your very own food truck, whipping up delicious dishes and dazzling desserts in Food Truck Chef™, the addictive FREE cooking game. Master the culinary arts with a vast array of ingredients, crafting amazing food from over 68 cuisines or dishes. From sizzling pasta and cheesy pizzas to delicate sushi and mouthwatering cakes & donuts, the possibilities are endless in your very own customizable food truck empire.

Why Choose Food Truck Chef™?

- Cook 800+ delectable dishes from around the world 
- Explore 20 exotic locations 
- Conquer 680+ fun and challenging levels 
- Compete against other chefs in food truck showdowns & Carnival cook-off
- Build your own food truck empire around the world

Sharpen Your Culinary cooking skills:

Master a variety of techniques, cooking everything from juicy nachos and falafel to sizzling kebabs, decadent desserts, and trendy ASMR treats. Perfect your skills with breads, pasta, noodles, and classic hot dogs.

Embark on a Global Culinary Journey:

Visit breathtaking locations like Pasta Street, Pizza Avenue, BBQ Boulevard, Waffle Way, Oriental Oasis, Baker's Lane, Coffee land, Sandwich Square, Sushi Strip, Spicy Tandoor, Popcorn pop and the vibrant Tasty Town.

Style Your Dream Food Truck:

Customize your truck to attract more customers and reduce wait times. Design your food truck experience with unique furniture, decorations, eye-catching menus, and even a bookrack to personalize your space. Start with a pasta truck, then expand to a sizzling BBQ truck, a cheesy pizza truck, a spicy Tex-Mex truck, a delightful bakery truck, and more!

Food Truck Wars!

Challenge other chefs in thrilling food truck showdowns at the Food Street Festival.

Party Time!

Fuel hungry partygoers at exciting gigs and earn valuable gems.

Level Up Your Game:

Unlock incredible achievements and upgrade your kitchen to cook faster, serve more customers, and gain valuable time to conquer even the most challenging levels. Don't overcook any dishes to level up you stats.

Reach for the Stars!

Collect stars and earn gems in the exciting weekly Star Haul event featuring new themes every week.

Star Tournament Leaderboard:

Take part is fun restaurant cooking levels to earn your chef status as a Master Chef, Executive Chef, Star Chef and various other in-game Chef titles to showcase your virtual kitchen management skills.

Join the Food Truck Chef™ Community!

Follow us on social media for the latest news and offers:

Facebook: @foodtruckchefgame
Instagram: @foodtruck.chef
Twitter: @myfoodtruckchef
Unleash Your Inner Chef!

Expand your culinary empire as you unlock new cuisines, create culinary masterpieces, and become the world-famous Food Truck Chef™ you've always dreamed of being.

The world awaits your culinary creations, so fire up the grill and let's get cooking!

raw_data.releaseNotes: We've optimized the game for smoother performance! Dive into new, engaging special events, experience updated balancing, and enjoy a more polished experience with various bug fixes.

apps.title: Fooducate: Nutrition Coach
apps.description:
Since 2010, Fooducate has been helping millions of people eat healthier, lose weight and improve their health.

• Recommended by doctors, dietitians, fitness trainers, and personal coaches 
• Apple's Best of the iPhone Health & Fitness category
• 1st prize - US Surgeon General Healthy App Challenge 
• Media praise: USAToday, NYTimes, Dr. Oz, Oprah, WSJ, ABC, FOX, etc.


THE BEST NUTRITION & HEALTH TRACKER
+ Log your food intake and exercise 
+ See the quality of calories
+ Count your macros: protein, fats, carbs
+ Analyze your sugar intake
+ Track your sleep, mood, and hunger levels
+ Enter your recipes and instamagically & see their nutritional value!
+ Seamlessly integrated with Apple Health

PERSONALIZE FOODUCATE
- set your desired weight loss rate
- keto diet coach
- low-carb advice & carb management
- lower your cholesterol, 
- discover foods for heart health
- eat to beat diabetes
- women's health (pregnancy, lactation,PCOS)
- dietary goals (non processed foods, vegetarian)
- avoid MSG, HFCS, GMOs and other ingredients
- low FODMAP diet
- Gluten free and other allergens
(Note: some personalization features require a premium account)

EAT FOR HEALTH!
Fooducate analyzes information found in product nutrition panels and ingredient lists. Scan to discover things manufacturers don't want you to notice:
- added sugars
- artificial sweeteners such as aspartame
- trans fats 
- high fructose corn syrup 
- MSG
- controversial food colorings 
- GMO - genetical modified organisms (premium feature) 
- additives and preservatives 
- and more... 

HUGE FOOD DATABASE
+ Scan hundreds of thousands of unique product barcodes 
+ Get a personalized nutrition grade (A, B, C, or D) for each food
+ Get suggestions for healthier foods based on what you scan

THE BEST DIET ADVICE
+ health & diet tips from nutrition professionals
+ weight loss suggestions
+ Motivation, love & support from the community

USER REVIEWS 
***** "I lost 55 pounds with this app!"
***** "Eating healthy is the easy way to lose weight. Thanks Fooducate!"
***** "I am learning so many helpful new things about healthy eating."
***** "Makes healthy food checking a breeze"
***** "Fooducate is undoubtedly the best weight loss coach I ever had."

Health App integration:
- import your exercise & sleep data from other apps and devices
- export your meal nutrition data - calories, carbs, and more

IN-APP PURCHASES:

* Pro
—> KETO & Low-carb diet
—> Diabetes, kidney disease, heart health, and more
—> Paleo, vegan, vegetarian diet
—> GMO warnings
—> Weekly health & diet tips
—> Priority support
—> No ads.
Subscription options: monthly auto-renew, annual auto-renew, one-time purchase

* Gluten & Allergies
—> Gluten-free diet
—> Uncover gluten and allergens in your food
—> Choose allergen free alternatives
—> Includes gluten, milk, lactose, soy, peanuts, tree nuts, eggs, fish, shellfish, sesame, and corn.
—> Priority support. 
Subscription options: monthly auto-renew, annual auto-renew, one-time purchase

* Diet Kickstart
one-time purchase 

* Pet Food 
one-time purchase

Notes:
Payment will be charged to your iTunes Account at confirmation of purchase. Subscription automatically renews unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24-hours before the end of the current period. Your account will be charged for renewal within 24-hours prior to the end of the current period, and identify the cost of the renewal. You can manage your subscriptions and turn off auto-renewal by going to your Account Settings after purchase. When your subscription ends, you can still use the app, without premium features

---
Our terms of use: www.fooducate.com/terms 
Our privacy policy: www.fooducate.com/privacy
Our website: www.fooducate.com
Questions or feedback support@fooducate.com
Disclaimer: Nutrition info is based on the U.S. system - please use at your own discretion in other regions

A new version of Fooducate is here! Here’s what’s new:

* Performance improvements and bug fixes

Thanks for using Fooducate! Have questions or feedback? Email us at support@fooducate.com for fast & friendly support.

apps.title: Olive - Holistic Food Scanner
apps.description:
Olive: Healthy Food Scanner - Premium Yuka Alternative & Ingredient Checker. Your Personal Guide to Eating Healthy

Looking for a food scanner that helps you eat healthy, avoid toxic additives, and find cleaner alternatives? Olive is the all-in-one healthy food scanner, ingredient checker, and food checker app that makes grocery shopping stress-free. Instantly scan barcodes to reveal whether a product contains gluten, synthetic additives, allergens, toxins, or hidden chemicals. Whether you’re vegan, managing food allergies, or just trying to avoid seed oils and processed sugar, Olive empowers you with transparency, knowledge, and healthier choices for you and your family.

◆ FEATURES OF OUR HEALTHY FOOD SCANNER*

1. Instant Food Scanner – Scan any barcode to check for harmful additives, seed oils, gluten, pesticides, toxins, or synthetic ingredients.

2. Ingredient Checker – Break down confusing food labels into clear insights. Easily spot hidden sugars, artificial colors, preservatives, and allergens.

3. Healthy Alternatives – Get personalized product suggestions that align with your lifestyle, whether you’re vegan, gluten-free, or allergy-sensitive.

4. Food Checker for Restaurants – Discover seed oil–free restaurants near you for cleaner, worry-free dining.

5. Lab-Tested Transparency – Go beyond surface-level info. Olive includes recall alerts, contaminant reports (PFAS, microplastics, heavy metals), and lab-tested data.

6. Community & Database – Access over 1 million products, with new items added daily thanks to a growing health-conscious community.

*features listed are accessible through the Olive Premium subscription

◆  BENEFITS OF USING A HEALTHY FOOD SCANNER APP

* Eat with confidence knowing what’s really in your food.
* Reduce exposure to harmful toxins, additives, and synthetic chemicals.
* Support your family’s health and boost energy, digestion, and immunity.
* Enjoy peace of mind dining out with our seed oil–free restaurant finder.

◆  WHY CHOOSE OLIVE OVER OTHER FOOD CHECKER APPS?

Unlike basic food scanner apps, Olive combines ingredient checking, toxin detection, and unbiased healthy alternatives. Many apps stop at flagging products, but Olive goes further:

* Unbiased results – No ads, no brand influence, no hidden sponsorships.
* Lab-tested reliability – Backed by scientific analysis and recall alerts.
* Holistic scope – Scan food, water, and cosmetics (coming soon) for harmful substances.


◆  HOW THE OLIVE FOOD SCANNER WORKS (3 SIMPLE STEPS)

* Scan – Point your camera at any food, drink, or household product barcode.
* Analyze – Instantly see a breakdown of ingredients, allergens, and toxins.
* Choose Better – Get safe, healthier alternatives tailored to your dietary needs.

◆ FAQS ABOUT THE OLIVE HEALTHY FOOD SCANNER

What is Olive?
Olive is a holistic healthy food scanner and ingredient checker app that helps you quickly scan food labels, detect toxins, and find cleaner alternatives.

Is Olive good for allergies?
Yes! Olive highlights allergens such as gluten, dairy, soy, and nuts—making it ideal for families with food sensitivities.

Does Olive only scan food?
No. Olive also checks bottled water for contaminants like fluoride and heavy metals, and soon you’ll be able to scan cosmetics and personal care products

Why is Olive the best food scanner?
Unlike other food checker apps, Olive uses lab-tested data, unbiased ratings, and a seed oil–free restaurant map to give you more transparency and healthier choices.

Join the hundreds of thousands switching from Yuka, Bobby Approved, Seed Oil Scout and other food scanner apps to Olive. Download today for safer, healthier grocery shopping and toxin-free living!

Olive – Scan Smarter. Shop Safer. Live Healthier.

Terms of Service: https://www.oliveapp.com/terms-of-service
Privacy Policy: https://www.oliveapp.com/privacy-policy
Apple licensed application end user license agreement (EULA): https://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/dev/stdeula/

apps.title: Lieferando.de
apps.description:
With the Lieferando iPhone app, you can order the food you love wherever you are in Germany. From over 37,000 restaurants, supermarkets and convenience stores to choose from, you can enjoy everything from burgers, pizza, pasta, sushi, salads and loads more, and get it all delivered to your door.

Need some bits from the supermarket, liquor store or florist? Just open the Lieferando app, choose ‘groceries’ and fill your basket. Whether it’s baby food, diapers, flowers, liquor, beer, wine, beauty products, ice cream, chocolate, milk, fruit and bread, our partners have it all.

How it works:
Ordering is easy. You can either pick a saved address, fill in your postcode/street name or let the app find your location automatically. You can then choose your favourite restaurant or store and select what you fancy. Choose to pay with PayPal, Klarna, credit card, Apple Pay or another option, or pay with cash when your food gets delivered if the restaurant allows it.

Follow your order to your doorstep:
Track your order from the kitchen or store straight to your doorstep with our Food Tracker®. We'll even send you push notifications to update you about the status of your order. It usually takes 30-45 minutes to deliver your food or groceries.

What you get with our app:
- Quick and hassle-free ordering
- Great offers and discounts
- Choose to pick up your order at the restaurant or store
- Re-order the same delicious meal with one tap of a button
- Browse grocery stores, cuisines, offers, best-rated restaurants, nearby spots and vegetarian/halal options
- Get regular updates on your order with our handy Food Tracker®
- Choose from multiple payment options like credit card, PayPal, Klarna and more


Our restaurant partners:
Order from big brands like McDonald’s, Pizza Hollywood, Akakiko, dean&david and Wiener Schnitzelland

Our grocery and convenience partners:
Order from supermarkets and other partners like Spar express.

Let us know what you think
Loving the app? If you have any tips, ideas or feedback, leave us a review or contact us at iosapp@takeaway.com.

Bon APPétit!

advisories: Infrequent/Mild Alcohol, Tobacco, or Drug Use or References
Infrequent/Mild Contests
raw_data.releaseNotes:
Your Lieferando app has a brand new look!

Based on your feedback, we improved the design. It’s easier than ever to order what you want – from groceries to delicious meals.
There are now more search options and filters, and we also improved the navigation speed.

On top of that, we added new features like:

- Loved in your area
Browse the most popular categories in your neighbourhood. 

- Bigger menu images
See what’s on offer at a glance. Like the look of something? Press ‘+’ to add it to your basket.

- Your cravings, saved
Your last order is saved for you, so you can come back to it anytime.

There are more exciting features coming up in the near future, so make sure you update your Lieferando app regularly!

Questions or tips? Contact us: iosapp@takeaway.com

apps.title: Yandex Go: Taxi Food Market
apps.description:
Yandex Go
Rides, Market, scooters, package and food delivery

• RIDES
Pick your service class
Ride Economy for everyday errands. Comfort and Comfort+ to relax with more legroom. Minivan for big groups, traveling with skis or bicycles, or trips to the airport.

• SCOOTERS
Bright yellow Yandex Go scooters are already cruising cities. Rent up to three scooters from the same account, buy Minute Bundles to make rides more affordable, and use Yandex Plus to subscribe to Scooters for free unlocks.

• FOOD FROM RESTAURANTS
Order delivery from independent and popular chain restaurants. Stock up on snacks for a party, soup, khachapuri, wok, sushi, pizza, and vegan options.

• MARKET YANDEX GO
Market Yandex Go offers dozens of categories and millions of important, useful items in Russia and Uzbekistan. Enjoy the user-friendly search or select the categories to find what you're looking for. Add items to your cart, place and track your order — all in the Yandex Go app.
If you've already added items to your Yandex Market cart, you'll see your order in Yandex Go and can continue checkout there. If an item is out of stock, we'll suggest alternatives at about the same price.

• DELIVERY
Have a courier pick up your printer after repairs, hand over documents to a contractor, or haul off that old couch you sold. For large items, you can order a cargo truck. Couriers will arrive for pickup in just 15 minutes.

• TRANSPORT
View schedules for buses, trams, commuter trains, and other public transport, compare routes, and find the nearest stops and convenient transfers. Available in some cities for now.
 
Availability of services and options may vary depending on the region.

raw_data.releaseNotes: It's time to update the app! We fixed a few bugs and made some minor improvements to make it a bit faster, but you won't see any visual changes.

apps.title: Food Diary See How You Eat Log
apps.description:
Looking for a simple app to track your meals? 

You have found the right app. 

Only 2 taps to log a meal. Try it yourself. 

The See How You Eat Food Diary app is a simple and easy-to-use photo food journal that helps you track your food and eat regularly while building healthy eating habits. 

FOOD TRACKING MADE SIMPLE, FUN & EFFECTIVE: 

1. See your daily meals at a glance 
2. Easy and straightforward to use —  take a photo to log your meals
3. Meal reminders
4. Feel more energetic  
5. Become mindful of your eating habits
6. Forget about diets and calorie counting
7. Simple to share your food diary with your coach or friends

With the See How You Eat Food Diary app, you can see at a glance all the meals you’ve had that day, compelling you to make healthy food choices. Photographing your meals encourages you to change your eating habits. Meal reminders help you with regular eating, and you’ll feel more energetic throughout the day. 

BENEFITS OF PHOTOGRAPHING MEALS: 

• You’ll see at a glance all the meals of the day
• An easy method to log your meals
• Taking photos of meals supports mindfulness
• Photo food diary helps you with changing your eating habits
• Photographing your meals encourages healthy food choices

BENEFITS OF REGULAR EATING: 

• Stay energetic throughout the day
• Supports intuitive and mindful eating
• Lose cravings for unhealthy foods 
• Get rid of sugar cravings

BENEFITS OF MEAL REMINDERS:

• Regular eating means you’re not continuously hungry
• Regular eating means you have more energy
• You learn intuitive eating naturally
• You become aware of your eating patterns 

BENEFITS OF KEEPING A FOOD DIARY:

• According to studies, keeping a food diary has multiple benefits
• People who keep a food journal report they make a healthy food choice
• Eat more vegetables and pay attention to the portion size
• Food tracking has multiple benefits for eating habits change 
• Recent studies confirm that photo food tracking raises awareness and changes dietary habits

BENEFITS OF VISUAL MEAL SUMMARY:

• Eating habits are much more than calorie counting 
• Meal plate photo makes you conscious of your nutritional choices
• Are you having vegetables or not?  
• How did you feel that day? Or before or after a meal?
• No detailed nutritional information is needed to see how you eat
• Save macros, nutrients, measurements, calorie counting, and detailed food & meal tracking for fitness athletes

STAY MOTIVATED
• Fun Challenges

WHY SEE HOW YOU EAT FOOD JOURNAL?

1. Beautiful daily meal college with meal time stamps
2. Super simple to use - just 2 taps to log a meal
3. Become mindful of your eating
4. Motivates without gimmicks
5. Stay on track with your eating rhythm
6. Meal reminders to help you with regular eating
7. Planning, tracking & sharing options (export your data)
8. Track your daily water intake or all daily drinks and goal progress
9. Simple to export your visual food diary with a professional (coach, personal trainer, nutritionist, or doctor)
10. You are free from endless diets and calorie-counting

Whether you want to feel better, be more energetic, be healthy and happy, or learn mindful eating, the Food Diary See How You Eat app helps you succeed. It’s the easiest way to track your meals and eat regularly! There is no reason to go hungry! 

Health Revolution Ltd develops simple & easy-to-use food tracking & nutrition coaching concepts. Our mission is to help people discover the basics of balanced eating habits that suit today’s hectic lifestyle. We are against calorie counting & crash diets. We stand for intuitive eating. Envisioning a world without dieting.

Subscription terms: 
See How You Eat Food Diary is a subscription app with a 7-day FREE trial. The SHYE app offers an auto-renewing subscription to provide unlimited access to all SHYE Premium features while maintaining an active subscription. 

More about terms & conditions here:
http://seehowyoueat.com/terms/
http://seehowyoueat.com/privacy-policy/

advisories: Infrequent/Mild Medical/Treatment Information

Whether you’re focusing on mindful eating, your fitness journey, food sensitivities, or working with a nutrition professional, See How You Eat is here to support you.

See How You Eat Food Diary – food tracking made simple, fun, and inspiring.

apps.title: Rappi - Deliveries in Minutes
apps.description:
TRY RAPPI TODAY

Get everything delivered in minutes. Discover the app that makes life simpler.

Rappi brings you the best selection of food, groceries, liquor, convenience items, pharmacy essentials, flowers, and so much more. With over 200,000 restaurants and stores in 300+ cities across Latin America, Rappi connects you with the best products in your city.

WHAT CAN YOU ORDER?

- Your favorite meals: Pizzas, burgers, bowls, sushi, and much more.
- Rappi Turbo for ultra-fast, 10-min deliveries: Over 8,000 everyday products and meals brought to your door in minutes.
- Groceries: Fresh items from top brands, handpicked by experts and delivered to your door.
- Pharmacy: Everything you need to take care of yourself, anytime.
- Liquor and convenience: Drinks, snacks, and more for your next gathering with friends or family.
- Pet care and gifts: Treat your furry friends or find the perfect gift from thousands of options.
- RappiFavor: Need a concierge? We'll pick up, buy or deliver anything for you. Quick and reliable task-based deliveries are here to help.
- Rappi Bank & Rappi Card: Credit card with no annual fees, cashback perks, and 24/7 support.
- Rappi Travel: Plan your next trip with exclusive deals on flights and hotels.

WHAT'S NEW WITH RAPPI

- Follow your friends: See their favorites, share recommendations, and connect over what you enjoy.
- Top recommendations: Discover local foodie picks from influencers, celebrities, and foodies across 9 countries.
- Exclusive offers just for you: Enjoy personalized discounts and offers, all in one place and tailored to your interests. 
- Rappi Turbo has more: More products, more categories, and now lower prices. Plus, you can now get your entire grocery list delivered in minutes.
- More precise searches: Find exactly what you’re looking for with AI-powered search.
- 24/7 10-min delivery stores: More Turbo stores are open around the clock. Order what you need, whenever you need it.
- And so much more: Update the app to explore all the latest features!

HOW IT WORKS

Browse everything the app has to offer, choose what you need, and get it delivered to your door in minutes with real-time tracking. Want it later? Schedule your delivery for the perfect time.

WHERE WE DELIVER

Rappi is available in Argentina, Brazil, Chile, Colombia, Costa Rica, Ecuador, Mexico, Peru, and Uruguay—connecting you with the best your city has to offer.

DOWNLOAD RAPPI AND REDEFINE HOW YOU EXPERIENCE YOUR CITY.

Savor the convenience of two incredible meal delivery experiences in one app. Meet Home Chef and Tempo - your go-to solutions for delicious, hassle-free meals that fit your lifestyle. The Home Chef app makes every step of ordering, cooking, and reviewing our simple, delicious meals even easier. 

Home Chef: Delicious, Meal Kit Magic
Whatever moments you’re tackling, Home Chef makes cooking dinner quick, tasty, and—above all else—easy. Every week, choose nearly 40 new recipes created by our chefs. You can also customize select recipes so you can make something fresh every single week. Home Chef makes delicious home cooking achievable.

Tempo: Fast, Feel-Good Meals

- Curated for You: Discover tailored meal recommendations that match your preferences and cravings.

FoodSpot is the app built specifically for food discovery, powered by our smart AI technologies. It recommends a feed of dishes rather than restaurants, thus a step closer to your decision on what to eat.

Other than smart food recommendation, you can also search for nearby dishes & restaurants if you already have your own preferences in mind, or you can browse a recommended list of dishes. apps.title: Shuttle: Food Delivery Korea
apps.description:
Food Delivery in Korea 


Order Food in Korea – Fast, Easy, and in English
Shuttle is Korea’s leading foreign-friendly food delivery app, trusted by expats, travelers, and the U.S. military community. Order food, groceries, and essentials from top local restaurants and shops—all in your language.


New users get ₩5,000 OFF their first order with code: SHUTTLE.


Key Features

· Local Eats, Delivered – Discover the best Korean and international restaurants near you.
· Seamless Pickups – Skip the line and collect your order with easy in-store pickup.
· Grocery Delivery – Get groceries, heat-to-eat meals, home essentials, and gifts with next-day delivery via Shuttle Market.
· English App & Support – No more language barriers! Order in English and get customer support via live chat.
· Multilingual App – Use the Shuttle app in your preferred language—now available in Korean (한국어), English, Vietnamese (Tiếng Việt), Thai (ภาษาไทย), Bahasa (Bahasa Indonesia), Japanese (日本語), Simplified Chinese (简体中文), Cantonese (粵語), French (Français), Spanish (Español), German (Deutsch), Arabic (العربية), Hindi (हिन्दी). *Please note: Menu content is currently available in English and Korean only. 
· Secure Payments – Pay with major international/Korean credit cards, PayPal, KakaoPay, or store your method for fast checkout.
· No Korean Phone Number Needed – Sign up with just an email, phone verification is optional (but required for using Shuttle credit).
· Shuttle e-Gifts – Send Shuttle credits to friends and family by email for birthdays, holidays, or just because.


Proudly Serving U.S. Military in Korea

Order easily near USAG Yongsan, Camp Humphreys, Osan Air Base, Kunsan Air Base, USAG Daegu, and more. Use your U.S. credit card  and enjoy trusted delivery from base-friendly restaurants.


Need Help?

Live chat is available in English or Korean. Or reach us at: info@shuttledelivery.co.kr

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/ShuttleDeliveryCo

apps.title: Yango: taxi, food, delivery
apps.description:
Yango is an easy-to-use app for getting around the city
Fill your life with movement. Get the whole city in your hands, ride wherever you want, and enjoy comfort at an affordable price. With Yango, everything is possible!

Choose the right service class for you
Reach your destination at the right level of comfort and price for you. Choose from several service classes. Economy is awesome for when you need a ride fast. Comfort lets you sit back and just enjoy the ride. And The Fastest is the best in case when the service class doesn’t matter and you just need the closest ride available!

Ride safely
Safety is our top priority. You’ll see who’s coming to pick you up and in which car right in the app. You’ll see info about the driver, such as their name and rating, and will be able to share your route with whomever you like so they know where you are.

Smart destinations
Yango will suggest destinations for your rides based on your ride history, like first offering ‘home’ as a destination because it’s your most common request on weekday evenings. Ride the smart way!

Multiple destinations, one route
Yango makes everyday life super easy. Like picking the kids up from school, dropping a friend off at a market, and doing some quick shopping on the way. Just add a new stop in the app, and Yango will recalculate a new route for the driver. 

Request rides for close ones
Show you care by requesting rides for friends and relatives. Get your mother to a doctor’s appointment, book a ride to pick up your special someone, or get each of your friends a ride home after a night out. You can request up to 3 cars at once.

Refer friends and get discounts
Invite friends to try Yango and save together. Share your personal promo code, get a discount on your next ride and grant your friend with an extra discount on their first ride. It’s as easy as that.

Meet Delivery - it's like a taxi service, but for your packages

We've also built in a fast delivery service into Yango - use Delivery to quickly send personal packages or even business orders by courier anywhere in the city. Delivery is suitable for any item that can be transported by scooter or car. 

An international service
Yango is a ride-hailing, mobility, and delivery aggregator service that operates in more than 20 countries around the world, including Ghana, Cote d'Ivoire, Cameroon, Senegal and Zambia.

Yango is an informational service and not a transportation or taxi services provider. Transportation services are provided by third parties.
The size and duration of the discount for the first rides requested via the Yango app vary depending on the country and city. Open the app for specific details.

Privacy Policy:
https://yango.com/legal/yango_privacy_notice
Yango Plus subscription conditions:
https://deli.yango.com/en-IL/about/docs/legal/yango_plus_conditions

apps.title: Kitchen Scramble: Cooking Game
apps.description:
Embark on a Culinary Adventure with Kitchen Scramble: Cooking Game!

Join Chef Pepper as she takes her food truck around the globe in this FREE, highly addictive time-management and cooking simulation game. Perfect for adults who love casual, stress-free gaming, Kitchen Scramble offers an immersive experience where your kitchen skills are put to the ultimate test.

Why You'll Love Kitchen Scramble:

- Become a Star Chef: Hone your cooking skills across diverse restaurant settings and master various cooking techniques. Serve your customers swiftly to earn high tips or risk losing them if you're too slow!

- Global Food Journey: Travel city by city around the world, preparing and serving a vast array of food. Delight your customers with dishes like Eggs Benedict, Szechuan Chicken, Sweet and Sour Shrimp, Pizzas, Hamburgers, and more!

- Extensive Menu: With over 1,500 delicious dishes crafted from 280+ high-quality ingredients, there's always something new to cook and serve.

- Challenging Time-Management: Navigate through 2,000+ levels set in 80+ unique locations. Balance speed and accuracy to meet customers' demands under various challenges, including timed levels and minimum score requirements.

- Upgrade Your Kitchen: Enhance your kitchen with 100+ appliances like coffee makers, rice cookers, pizza ovens, and waffle makers. Upgrades help you manage the food line more efficiently and expand your food offerings.

- Social Features: Connect with friends on Facebook to share progress, unlock new locations, and compete on global leaderboards. Ask for help to progress faster and share your culinary achievements on social media!

Exciting Features:

- 1,500+ Dishes: Cook a wide variety of food using the best ingredients.
- 2,000+ Levels: Complete challenges in 80+ locations worldwide.
- 100+ Upgrades: Improve your kitchen appliances to boost efficiency.
- Social Connectivity: Engage with friends, compete globally, and share your success.
- Power-ups & Boosters: Utilize special tools to manage your time and cook more effectively.
- Premium Ingredients: Use high-quality ingredients to earn bigger tips and satisfy demanding customers.

Join the Cooking Craze!

If you're passionate about cooking, kitchen management, and food simulation games, Kitchen Scramble is the perfect match for you. Whether you're multitasking in a bustling food truck or perfecting a gourmet meal in a high-end restaurant, every moment is packed with culinary excitement.

Ready to Cook? Grab your spatula and start mixing, frying, and sautéing with Chef Pepper today!

Download Now for FREE and Start Your Culinary Journey!

Stay Connected:
- Like us on Facebook: www.facebook.com/kitchenscramble
- Share your achievements and invite friends to join the fun!

Note:
- The game is FREE with optional in-app purchases to enhance your gameplay. You can disable or limit in-app purchases in your device settings.
- Push notifications keep you updated with gifts and new content releases. You can disable them in your device settings if preferred.

apps.title: Nutrition Tracker: Foodnoms
apps.description:
Foodnoms is a nutrition tracker designed to be fast, powerful, and easy to use. Set custom nutrition goals, log your food, and measure your progress.

HOW IT WORKS
1. Log what you eat and drink with a fast, beautiful interface.
2. Set specific nutrition goals for calories, macros (protein, fat, carbohydrates), net carbs, cholesterol, fiber, sugars, water, alcohol, caffeine, and more.
3. Learn about your nutrition, and use that knowledge to reach your health and fitness goals.

LEARN ABOUT YOUR NUTRITION
• Track your success for each of your goals over time
• Discover which foods are helping you and which ones are holding you back
• Automatic tracking of intermittent fasts

FAST LOGGING
• Scan barcodes and nutrition labels
• Save time using Smart Suggestions, which recommends foods to log based on your food habits
• Log food and check on your goals with Siri and the Shortcuts app
• Leave the food scale at home and instead record the accuracy of your recordings

BEAUTIFUL HOME SCREEN WIDGETS
• Track your nutrition and fasting goals right from your Home Screen
• Quickly log food and open the label scanner

WORKS WITH APPLE HEALTH
• Read and write nutrition data to the Health app - calories, macros, vitamins, minerals, water, caffeine and more
• Use Active Energy data from the Health app (i.e. the Move ring on the Apple Watch) to automatically adjust your calorie goal

BUILT TO PROTECT YOUR PRIVACY
• Sync your data to multiple devices securely with iCloud and the Health app
• No advertisements or spam
• Transparent privacy policy

TRUSTWORTHY NUTRITION DATA
• A food database with hundreds of thousands of food items with rich nutrition data from trustworthy sources
• Quickly scan nutrition labels to quickly log accurate data for packaged foods
• Create custom foods, recipes, and meals, and share them with your friends

ACCESSIBILITY
• Dynamic type support
• Dark mode

FOODNOMS+ VS FREE
• Free - unlimited food tracking; create goals for calories and macros; create recipes and meals; integration with the Health app; basic notifications; CSV export
• Foodnoms+ - log drinks; track water, sodium, fiber, net carbs, caffeine, alcohol, and more; recipe import; AI meal scanner; create custom meal types; Foodnoms AI; save commonly-eaten items as favorites; import nutrition data from Health; view more stats and charts; track intermittent fasts; plus other exclusive features

Terms of Use: https://foodnoms.com/terms

apps.title: getir: groceries, food&beyond
apps.description:
Experience unparalleled convenience with Getir. Getir delivers your daily essentials - fresh ingredients, delightful restaurant meals, and even that last-minute birthday card - directly to your doorstep in minutes. Plus, say goodbye to waiting in line for a taxi. With thousands of services available at your fingertips, Getir frees up your time and takes care of the errands, making life simpler.

Discover thousands of products instantly with Getir, spanning categories like Snacks, Water & Beverages, Ice Cream, Baked Goods, Home Care, Personal Care, and Pet Products. Getir, Turkey's premier delivery app, caters to your immediate needs. Say goodbye to trips to the store; let the store come to you!

Experience effortless shopping with GetirMore! Browse thousands of products from diverse categories without the need to step foot in a store. Our couriers will deliver everything right to your door! From electronics to automotive supplies, sports gear, and beyond, enjoy a wide selection of products backed by n11 quality. Say goodbye to grocery runs, simply place your order and let GetirMore take care of the rest! 

Getir not only covers your grocery needs but also satisfies your cravings with delicious meals delivered to your doors with GetirFood! Enjoy swift delivery from nearby restaurants whenever you're hungry. We're here to bring quality meals from top restaurants, just a tap away! With both cash and online payment options available, satisfying your cravings has never been easier!

Explore a universe of local shopping with GetirLocals! From your neighborhood butcher, greengrocer, bakery, pet shop, electronics store, to herbalist, we've got you covered. Additionally, with GetirWater, you can have freshness delivered to your door with just a tap. Our aim is to simplify your daily life with fast and local support.

Getir goes beyond groceries and food; it's your solution for transportation too! With Bitaxi, hail a taxi to anywhere you want, and with GetirDrive, easily rent nearby vehicles for smooth rides. And when your journey ends, just find a convenient spot to park!

Get your groceries, food, and water delivered in minutes with Getir! Experience ultimate convenience with our fast, reliable, and seamless delivery service. Order with just a tap, and enjoy big savings with our wide variety of promotions on food and grocery orders. Plus, benefit from 24/7 live support for any questions or concerns.

Lightning-fast delivery
Mouthwatering food
Effortless online ordering
Thousands of products
Taxi and vehicle support
Outstanding deals
Fresh and high-quality products
Flexible payment options
User-friendly interface

raw_data.releaseNotes: We update the app regularly so we can make it better for you. Get the latest version for all of the features and improvements. Thanks for using Getir

apps.title: Food Platform 3D
apps.description:
You have a group of people and a limited supply of food.

You need to distribute food in such a way that all people were fed and satisfied.

If someone eats more, then someone else will eat less.

If a person is hungry for a long time, he will die!

Enjoy your game!

apps.title: BitePal: AI Calorie Tracker
apps.description:
Meet BitePal! The app to make healthy eating habits easy and fun. Track your meals to feed and raise your raccoon.
We believe that a lasting healthy relationship with food starts with being mindful about what you eat and how it impacts you.

Why BitePal?

No tedious calorie counting. Track food and get bite-sized insights based on your meal. No diets, no restrictions, no stress, no anxiety. ADHD friendly!

Track food with just a snap. No manual input, finally. You take a photo of your meal — AI magic does the rest.

Stay motivated to continue tracking everyday by feeding your raccoon.

Be Supported. Your Raccoon is always at your side. No shame or guilt about food. Love yourself whatever you’ve eaten. You’re always good.

Have Fun. Never get bored with your Raccoon’s comments and jokes because they’re always unique and never repetitive.


Try Intermittent Fasting.
Discover a flexible fasting tracker built right into BitePal. Pick your fasting window, follow your progress, and let your Raccoon cheer you on. No pressure — just another fun way to explore mindful eating.

Download BitePal! Your raccoon is already hungry!


Terms and conditions:
https://bitepal.app/terms
Privacy policy:
https://bitepal.app/privacy

apps.title: Cooking Diary® Restaurant Game
apps.description:
BECOME THE RULING CHEF OF A CULINARY EMPIRE AND JOIN THE BEST COOKING GAME, LOVED BY MILLIONS OF PLAYERS AROUND THE WORLD! FUN, IMMERSIVE, AND FREE!

Return to your hometown to revive your grandfather's culinary legacy and rise from humble beginnings to become a top chef. Along the way, experience both personal and professional growth as you embrace self-expression and develop your unique style. Become part of the family as you rebuild and strengthen the bonds that connect you. Together, bring the family business back to its former glory—help your grandfather save the family restaurant chain, restore your family's good name, and honor the values that unite you all.

Here's the recipe for Cooking Diary's success:

● Hundreds of appetizing dishes that make your mouth water!
● Dozens of unique restaurants: manage them skillfully and win gourmets' hearts!
● Trendy outfits to express yourself every day!
● Culinary competitions with generous prizes!
● Cute, unique pets that will never leave you bored!
● Interesting characters, each with their own personality!
● Fascinating storyline garnished with humor!
● Vibrant graphics and unparalleled animation!
● Regular fun and free updates!

Play with your friends, meet new ones, and etch YOUR NAMES into the culinary history of the city together!

Winner of the WEBBY PEOPLE'S VOICE AWARD 2020 for Strategy/Simulation Game
International Mobile Gaming Awards 2019 People's Choice Award winner

Cooking Diary is a free game, so you don't need to pay to download it, update it, or progress through the game. However, some game elements can be purchased with real money, including random items. You can disable in-app purchases in your device's settings.

apps.title: FoodieLens - Food Photo Editor
apps.description:
With over 440,000 downloads, FoodieLens is revolutionizing the way food photography is captured. This app allows anyone to create professional-looking photos of their meals with just a few taps. 

Specially designed for capturing the beauty and detail of food at close range, FoodieLens combines advanced technology with user-friendly functionality. 

Whether you aim to be the star of social media or simply want to preserve your culinary creations, FoodieLens empowers you to take stunning food photographs easily.

--------------------
Key Features:
--------------------
-> Extensive Filter Collection: With around 90 unique filters at your fingertips, transform any ordinary meal into a photographic masterpiece. Whether aiming for a classic black-and-white elegance or a vibrant retro vibe, these filters adjust your photos in a single tap to exude professional flair.

-> Creative Effects: Tap into creativity with about 50 artistic effects that can pixelate, sketch, distort, or cartoonize your images, offering endless possibilities for innovation in your food photography.

-> DSLR-Style Focus: Achieve that soft, blurred background seen in DSLR photographs with our focus tool, enhancing the visual appeal of your food by drawing attention to its details.

-> Precision Editing Controls: Manipulate brightness, color saturation, and hue with precision tools to ensure your food looks as delicious digitally as it does on your plate.

-> One-Tap Auto Adjust: Simplify photo editing with an auto-adjust feature that optimizes your photos with just one tap, ensuring they always look their best.

-> Scene-Specific Optimization: Whether you’re shooting indoors, at night, or outdoors, FoodieLens provides tailored adjustments to suit various lighting and environmental conditions, making sure your photos always have the right exposure and mood.

-> Fun Stickers and Text Options: Embellish your photos with an extensive selection of stickers or add text to narrate your food story. These decorative elements are perfect for adding a personal touch to your culinary snapshots.

-> Interactive Drawing: Unleash your creativity by drawing directly on your photos, adding unique touches that make your images one-of-a-kind.

-> Kaleidoscope and 3D Effects: Explore the unusual by turning your photos into fascinating kaleidoscope patterns or preparing them for an immersive experience with 3D glasses.

-> Comprehensive Photo Editing Tools: Resize, crop, rotate, and more—FoodieLens offers all the tools you need to perfect your photos. For those who like to control every aspect of their image, the tone curve adjustment offers complex editing capabilities that cater to advanced photographers.

-> User-Friendly Interface: Despite its range of professional-grade features, FoodieLens is designed to be intuitive and easy to use. Whether you’re a novice or an expert, you’ll find the interface straightforward and the results impressive.

FoodieLens is not just an app but a gateway to transforming your culinary experiences into lasting visual memories. It stands out in the crowded field of image editing apps by focusing specifically on food photography, offering tools and features that enhance the unique qualities of food. Let's capture the perfect shot of your next meal and share it with the world with FoodieLens!

raw_data.releaseNotes:
We're excited to bring you the latest update for FoodieLens! We've been hard at work making improvements to ensure you have the best experience possible. Here's what's new:

Optimized Ad Display: We've refined the placement and timing of ads to provide a smoother and more enjoyable experience. No more interruptions at inconvenient moments—just seamless use of your favorite features.

Code Cleanup: Our developers have meticulously gone through the code to remove any unnecessary elements. This cleanup not only improves performance but also ensures the app runs more efficiently.

Localization Enhancements: We've improved some of the localized texts that previously seemed unnatural. Now, the app speaks your language more fluently, providing a more intuitive and user-friendly experience.

We hope you enjoy these updates! As always, we're committed to making FoodieLens the best it can be. If you have any feedback or suggestions, feel free to reach out to us.
